%5B%7B%22title%22%3A%22Over%2042%25%20SC%2C%20ST%20Families%20Poor%2C%20Says%20Bihar%20Caste%20Survey%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20second%20tranche%20of%20data%20from%20the%20Bihar%20government's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ftopic%2Fcaste-census%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecaste-based%20survey%3C%2Fa%3E%20-%20and%20the%20full%20report%20on%20the%20economic%20condition%20of%20215%20Scheduled%20Castes%2C%20Scheduled%20Tribes%2C%20Backward%20Classes%20and%20Extremely%20Backward%20Classes%20-%20was%20tabled%20in%20the%20Assembly%20this%20afternoon.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20report%2C%20more%20than%2042%20per%20cent%20of%20families%20from%20Scheduled%20Castes%20and%20Scheduled%20Tribes%20are%20poor%2C%20as%20are%20over%2033%20per%20cent%20of%20those%20from%20Backward%20and%20Extremely%20Backward%20Classes.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAnd%2025.09%20per%20cent%20of%20General%20Category%20families%20are%20similarly%20listed.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOf%20those%20surveyed%2C%20less%20than%20six%20per%20cent%20of%20Scheduled%20Castes%20had%20finished%20their%20schooling%3B%20i.e.%2C%20Class%2011%20and%20Class%2012%2C%20while%20that%20number%20rises%20marginally%20to%20nine%20per%20cent%20across%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20first%20set%20of%20data%20was%20released%20last%20month%20and%20triggered%20a%20row%20between%20the%20ruling%20Janata%20Dal%20(United)-Rashtriya%20Janata%20Dal%20alliance%20and%20the%20opposition%2C%20which%20includes%20the%20BJP%2C%20a%20former%20JDU%20ally.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThat%20report%20said%20over%2060%20per%20cent%20of%20Bihar's%20population%20belong%20to%20Backward%20or%20Extremely%20Backward%20Classes%2C%20and%20more%20than%2020%20per%20cent%20come%20from%20Scheduled%20Castes%20or%20Scheduled%20Tribes.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%20%7C%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fbihar-caste-survey-out-27-backward-classes-36-extremely-backward-classes-4442234%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBihar%20Caste%20Survey%3A%2027%25%20Backward%20Classes%2C%2036%25%20Extremely%20Backward%20Classes%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Ch2%3EEconomic%20Data%3C%2Fh2%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20overall%20data%20from%20the%20Bihar%20government's%20report%20is%20worrying.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIt%20states%20that%2034.13%20per%20cent%20of%20all%20families%20in%20the%20state%20earn%20up%20to%20a%20paltry%20Rs%206%2C000%20per%20month%20and%2029.61%20per%20cent%20survive%20on%20Rs%2010%2C000%20or%20less.%20It%20also%20states%20that%20nearly%2028%20per%20cent%20live%20on%20income%20between%20Rs%2010%2C000%20and%20Rs%2050%2C000%2C%20and%20only%20less%20than%20four%20per%20cent%20earn%20over%20Rs%2050%2C000%20per%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20report%20paints%20a%20grim%20picture%20-%20particularly%20in%20a%20state%20where%20those%20from%20marginalised%20communities%20and%20backward%20classes%20constitute%20over%2080%20per%20cent%20of%20a%20population%20of%20more%20than%2013.1%20crore.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOverall%2C%2042.93%20per%20cent%20of%20families%20from%20Scheduled%20Castes%20and%2042.70%20per%20cent%20from%20Scheduled%20Tribes%20have%20been%20listed%20as%20poverty-stricken.%20Among%20Backward%20and%20Extremely%20Backward%20Classes%2C%20this%20number%20is%2033.16%20per%20cent%20and%2033.58%20per%20cent.%20Among%20other%20castes%2C%2023.72%20per%20cent%20of%20all%20families%20are%20poor.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%20%7C%3C%2Fstrong%3E%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fbihar-caste-based-survey-ndtv-explains-4443519%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ENDTV%20Explainer%3A%20With%20Eye%20On%20Polls%2C%20Breaking%20Down%20Bihar's%20Caste%20Survey%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOnly%2025.09%20per%20cent%20of%20General%20Category%20families%20are%20listed%20as%20poor.%20Within%20this%2C%2025.32%20per%20cent%20of%20Bhumihars%2C%2025.3%20per%20cent%20of%20Brahmins%2C%20and%2024.89%20per%20cent%20of%20Rajputs%20are%20listed%20as%20poor.%20Brahmins%20and%20Rajputs%20account%20for%207.11%20per%20cent%20of%20Bihar's%20population.%20The%20Bhumihars%20are%202.86%20per%20cent.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAmong%20Backward%20Classes%2C%2035.87%20per%20cent%20of%20Yadavs%20-%20Deputy%20Chief%20Minister%20Tejashwi%20Yadav%20belongs%20to%20this%20community%20-%20are%20poor%2C%20as%20are%2034.32%20per%20cent%20of%20Kushwahas%20and%2029.9%20per%20cent%20of%20Kurmis.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-10%2Fjd3io1t_bihar-caste-survey-report-1_625x300_02_October_23.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Yadavs%20constitute%2014.26%20per%20cent%20of%20the%20population%20and%20they%20are%20the%20largest%20OBC%20sub-group%2C%20while%20the%20other%20account%20for%20a%20little%20over%20eight%20per%20cent%20of%20the%20total.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOn%20average%2C%20over%2030%20per%20cent%20of%20EBC%20families%20are%20poor.%20It%20is%2029.87%20per%20cent%20among%20Telis%2C%20rising%20to%2032.99%20for%20Kanus%2C%2034.08%20for%20Chandravanshis%2C%2034.75%20for%20Dhanuks%20and%2035.88%20for%20Noniyas.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Ch2%3ELiteracy%20In%20Bihar%3C%2Fh2%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20overall%20literacy%20rate%20in%20the%20state%20is%2079.7%20per%20cent.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOnly%2022.67%20per%20cent%20of%20respondents%20had%20studied%20till%20Class%205%2C%20but%20this%20increases%20to%2024.31%20per%20cent%20for%20people%20from%20Scheduled%20Castes%20and%2024.65%20per%20cent%20for%20those%20from%20Extremely%20Backward%20Classes.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAmong%20the%20General%20Category%20this%20is%20just%2017.45%20per%20cent.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOnly%205.76%20per%20cent%20of%20those%20surveyed%20from%20Scheduled%20Castes%20had%20completed%20schooling%3B%20i.e.%2C%20Class%2011%20and%2012.%20This%20improved%20marginally%20to%20nine%20per%20cent%20for%20all%20respondents.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EDemands%20for%20a%20nation-wide%20caste%20census%20have%20gathered%20steam%20since%20Bihar's%20August%20survey%2C%20with%20the%20issue%20becoming%20a%20political%20hot%20potato%20in%20the%20run-up%20to%20elections%20in%20five%20states%20-%20Chhattisgarh%2C%20Telangana%2C%20Rajasthan%2C%20Madhya%20Pradesh%2C%20and%20Mizoram%20-%20this%20month%20and%20the%202024%20Lok%20Sabha%20poll.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20-%20at%20the%20centre%20-%20has%2C%20in%20the%20past%2C%20been%20reluctant%20to%20back%20this%20demand%2C%20but%20Union%20Home%20Minister%20Amit%20Shah%20indicated%20an%20about-face%20in%20that%20policy%20this%20week.%20He%20said%20his%20party%20had%20never%20really%20opposed%20the%20exercise%20but%20would%20only%20carry%20out%20a%20survey%20after%20due%20diligence.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%20%7C%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcaste-census-takes-centre-stage-with-amit-shah-saying-bjp-never-opposed-it-4543992%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAmid%20Opposition's%20Caste%20Census%20Push%2C%20Amit%20Shah%20Says%20BJP%20Never%20Opposed%20Idea%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20release%20of%20the%20first%20tranche%20of%20Bihar%20data%2C%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20had%2C%20in%20an%20event%20in%20poll-bound%20Madhya%20Pradesh%2C%20hit%20out%20at%20those%20%26quot%3Btrying%20to%20divide%20the%20country%20in%20the%20name%20of%20caste%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20has%20been%20clear%20on%20its%20position%3B%20it%20will%20hold%20a%20survey%20in%20states%20it%20wins%20in%20this%20month's%20polls%20and%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20said%20it%20will%20also%20be%20held%20at%20a%20national%20level%20should%20the%20party%20win%20next%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ENDTV%20is%20now%20available%20on%20WhatsApp%20channels.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.whatsapp.com%2Fchannel%2F0029Va4lixw7z4kcvZI9JM12%5C%22%3EClick%20on%20the%20link%3C