Pradesh%20and%20Rajasthan%20is%20a%20key%20factor%20behind%20the%20massive%20spike%20in%20Delhi's%20air%20pollution%20every%20winter.%20It%20asked%20the%20state%20governments%20to%20take%20steps%20to%20stop%20stubble%20burning.%20%26quot%3BWe%20want%20it%20stopped.%20We%20don't%20know%20how%20you%20do%20it%2C%20it's%20your%20job.%20But%20it%20must%20be%20stopped.%20Something%20has%20to%20be%20done%20immediately%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20court%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20did%20not%20spare%20Delhi%20government%20either.%20%26quot%3BDelhi%20government%20also%20must%20be%20responsible.%20There%20are%20many%20buses%20running%20that%20pollute%20and%20run%20at%20half%20capacity.%20You%20have%20to%20attend%20to%20the%20problem%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20bench%20of%20Justice%20SK%20Kaul%20and%20Justice%20Sudhanshu%20Dhulia%20posted%20the%20matter%20for%20Friday.%20The%20court%20has%20asked%20Centre%20to%20hold%20a%20meeting%20with%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20Rajasthan%2C%20Haryana%2C%20Punjab%20and%20Delhi%20governments%20on%20ways%20to%20stop%20stubble%20burning.%20It%20has%20also%20said%20it%20will%20look%20at%20vehicular%20emissions%2C%20another%20key%20contributor%20to%20Delhi's%20air%20pollution.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20was%20hearing%20a%20case%20flagging%20the%20toxic%20air%20quality%20in%20the%20national%20capital%2C%20which%20has%20been%20in%20the%20'severe'%20category%20over%20the%20past%20few%20days.%20According%20to%20the%20Central%20Pollution%20Control%20Board%20data%2C%20several%20areas%20in%20Delhi%20had%20an%20AQI%20of%20over%20400%20today%2C%20four%20times%20the%20satisfactory%20air%20quality%20level.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAppearing%20for%20the%20petitioner%2C%20Advocate%20Aparajita%20Singh%20said%20the%20farm%20fires%20in%20Punjab%20have%20not%20been%20checked.%20She%20said%20stubble%20burning%20is%20the%20top%20contributor%20to%20the%20slide%20in%20Delhi's%20air%20quality.%20%26quot%3BCAQM%20(Commission%20for%20Air%20Quality%20Management)%20and%20states%20are%20saying%20they%20are%20taking%20all%20steps%20to%20control%20air%20pollution.%20But%20stubble%20burning%20is%20still%20on%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20The%20court%20said%20Delhi%20%26quot%3Bcannot%20continue%20like%20this%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESenior%20Advocate%20Gopal%20Shankaranarayan%2C%20also%20appearing%20for%20petitioners%2C%20said%20this%20matter%20is%20being%20heard%20since%202017%20and%20several%20orders%20have%20been%20passed.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20also%20asked%20Punjab%20and%20Centre%20to%20look%20for%20an%20alternative%20crop%20to%20paddy.%20It%20flagged%20how%20paddy%20is%20also%20destroying%20the%20state's%20water%20table.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20annual%20spike%20in%20Delhi's%20air%20pollution%20levels%20and%20the%20role%20of%20stubble%20burning%20behind%20it%20has%20emerged%20as%20a%20politically%20charged%20issue%20over%20the%20past%20few%20years.%20The%20Aam%20Aadmi%20Party%20government%20in%20Delhi%20has%20earlier%20accused%20rivals'%20governments%20in%20Punjab%20and%20Haryana%20for%20not%20cracking%20down%20on%20the%20burning%20of%20crop%20residue.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20AAP%20finds%20itself%20in%20a%20tricky%20position%20now%20as%20it%20rules%20both%20Delhi%20and%20Punjab.%20It%20has%20claimed%20that%20stubble%20burning%20in%20Punjab%20has%20seen%20a%20big%20drop%20and%20shifted%20blame%20to%20BJP-ruled%20Haryana.%C2%A0Delhi%20Environment%20Minister%20Gopal%20Rai%20has%20said%20the%20BJP%20is%20scapegoating%20Punjab%2C%20while%20their%20governments%20have%20failed%20to%20ban%20diesel%20buses%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20and%20Haryana.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20has%20slammed%20the%20Arvind%20Kejriwal%20government%2C%20questioning%20the%20rationale%20behind%20announcing%20the%20odd-even%20scheme%20after%20Diwali%20and%20several%20other%20steps%20to%20check%20the%20air%20pollution%20in%20the%20capital.%C2%A0The%20effectiveness%20of%20the%20odd-even%20scheme%20was%20not%20backed%20by%20any%20research%20and%20it%20was%20being%20implemented%20as%20a%20%26quot%3Bpublicity%20stunt%26quot%3B%2C%20Delhi%20BJP%20president%20Virendra%20Sachdeva%20has%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20farmers%20have%20their%20reasons%20to%20burn%20the%20crop%20residue.%20They%20are%20pressed%20for%20time%20ahead%20of%20the%20winter%20sowing%20season%20and%20setting%20fire%20to%20the%20farms%20is%20the%20fastest%20and%20cheapest%20way%20to%20clear%20the%20field%20for%20the%20new%20crops.%20The%20alternative%20is%20to%20rope%20in%20labourers%20or%20machines%20to%20do%20to%20the%20job%20-%20both%20requiring%20considerable%20funds.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1699344720000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2021-11%2Ftirjtkjg_stubble-burningpunjabpti-_625x300_13_November_21.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fdelhi-news%2Fdelhi-air-pollution-murder-of-public-health-supreme-courts-big-remark-4552833%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Air%20pollution%20in%20Delhi%20can't%20become%20a%20political%20battle%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20said%20today%2C%20stressing%20that%20the%20choking%20air%20quality%20is%20responsible%20for%20the%20%26quot%3Bmurder%20of%20people's%20health%26quot%3B.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fdelhi-news%2Fdelhi-air-pollution-murder-of-public-health-supreme-courts-big-remark-4552833%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fdelhi-news%2Fdelhi-air-pollution-murder-of-public-health-supreme-courts-big-remark-4552833%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fdelhi-news%2Fdelhi-air-pollution-murder-of-public-health-supreme-courts-big-remark-4552833%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Watch%3A%20Mathews%20Shares%20'Video%20Proof'%2C%20Proves%20Umpire's%20Timed%20Out%20Call%20Wrong%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ESri%20Lanka%20all-rounder%20Angelo%20Mathews%20became%20the%20victim%20of%20