ence%20degree%20in%20Data%20Science%20and%20AI%20and%20a%20two-year%20Master%20of%20Technology%20degree%20in%20Data%20Science%20and%20AI.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Zanzibar%20campus%20was%20inaugurated%20by%20His%20Excellency%20Dr%20Hussein%20Ali%20Mwinyi%2C%20President%20of%20Zanzibar%20and%20Chairman%20of%20the%20Revolutionary%20Council%20in%20the%20presence%20of%20Tanzanian%20officials%2C%20Indian%20dignitaries%2C%20faculty%20and%20students.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20campus%20was%20inaugurated%20in%20the%20presence%20of%20Prof%20Adolf%20F%20Mkenda%2C%20Minister%20of%20Education%20Science%20and%20Technology%20United%20Republic%20of%20Tanzania%2C%20Hon%20Binaya%20Srikanta%20Pradhan%2C%20India%20High%20Commissioner%20of%20The%20United%20Republic%20of%20Tanzania%2C%20Lela%20Mohamed%20Mussa%2C%20Minister%20of%20Education%20and%20Vocational%20Training-Zanzibar%2C%20Prof%20M%20S%20Ananth%20and%20Prof%20Bhaskar%20Ramamurthi%2C%20former%20Directors%20of%20IIT%20Madras%2C%20Prof%20Preeti%20Aghalayam%2C%20Dean%20of%20School%20of%20Engineering%20and%20Science%2C%20and%20Director-in-charge%2C%20Zanzibar%20campus%2C%20IIT%20Madras%2C%20faculty%2C%20students%2C%20staff%20and%20others.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20campus%20has%20been%20launched%20with%20the%20government's%20aim%20to%20take%20top%20quality%20education%20system%20of%20India%20to%20international%20arenas.%20The%20campus%20has%20been%20built%20in%20Bweleo%20district%2C%20located%20approximately%2015%20km%20south%20of%20Zanzibar%20town%20and%20is%20equipped%20with%20international%20amenities%20designed%20to%20meet%20the%20current%20needs%20of%20students.%20A%20permanent%20campus%20will%20be%20built%20soon%20jointly%20by%20the%20Government%20of%20Zanzibar%20and%20the%20Government%20of%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20campus%20has%20been%20designed%20to%20accommodate%20students%20in%20dorms%20and%20provide%20various%20facilities%20such%20as%20offices%2C%20classrooms%20and%20auditoriums%2C%20dining%20and%20a%20dispensa