20the%20Yadavs%20and%20Muslims.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHe%20added%2C%20%E2%80%9CNitish%20Kumar%20has%20done%20so%20under%20the%20pressure%20of%20Lalu%20Prasad%20Yadav%20to%20appease%20the%20Muslims%20and%20undermine%20the%20extremely%20backward%20classes.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20clear%20that%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20leader%20who%20is%20regarded%20as%20number%20two%20only%20to%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20said%20this%20in%20an%20apparent%20bid%20to%20give%20a%20communal%20twist%20to%20the%20exercise.%20His%20goal%20could%20have%20also%20been%20to%20create%20confusion%20among%20the%20extremely%20backward%20classes%20or%20EBCs%2C%20who%20are%20largely%20understood%20to%20be%20sympathetic%20to%20the%20opposition%20now.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBut%20Shah%E2%80%99s%20claim%20seems%20to%20be%20incorrect%20in%20the%20context%20of%20facts%20and%20data%20too.%20The%20caste%20survey%20report%20has%20put%20the%20EBCs%20at%2036.1%25.%20The%20Other%20Backward%20Classes%20are%20at%2027.12%25.%20Yadavs%20are%20a%20part%20of%20OBCs%2C%20and%20are%2014.26%25.%20Muslims%20are%2017.7%25%20of%20the%20population%20in%20Bihar.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20theory%20of%20%E2%80%98appeasement%E2%80%99%20strikes%20as%20odd%20once%20you%20consider%20empirical%20analysis%20of%20the%20reality%2C%20which%20shows%20that%20the%20Hindutva%20party%20has%20subjected%20Muslims%20to%20significant%20neglect.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EFor%20instance%2C%20the%20BJP%20did%20not%20offer%20a%20single%20ticket%20to%20Muslims%20of%20the%20state%20in%20the%202019%20Lok%20Sabha%20and%202020%20assembly%20elections.%20It%20has%20few%20Muslims%20in%20its%20cadre%20structure%20from%20the%20top%20to%20bottom.%20Compared%20to%20this%2C%20the%20Rashtriya%20Janata%20Dal%20and%20Janata%20Dal%20(United)%20have%20had%20representation%20of%20minorities%20in%20the%20legislature%20and%20executive%20of%20the%20government%2C%20as%20well%20as%20in%20its%20cadre%20structure.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EReacting%20to%20Shah%E2%80%99s%20claims%20of%20%E2%80%98appeasement%E2%80%99%2C%20Bihar%20deputy%20chief%20minister%20Tejashwi%20Yadav%2C%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CIf%20they%20%5BBJP%5D%20feel%20that%20the%20Bihar%20caste%20survey%20has%20inflated%20the%20number%20of%20the%20Yadavs%20and%20Muslims%2C%20they%20should%20conduct%20the%20Caste%20Census%20at%20the%20national%20level.%20Who%20is%20stopping%20them%3F%20Shah%20is%20trying%20to%20give%20a%20communal%20twist%20to%20the%20exercise%20that%20we%20have%20done%20to%20uplift%20the%20socially%20and%20economically%20backward%20sections%20of%20the%20society.%20His%20communal%20card%20won%E2%80%99t%20work%20whatever%20he%20does%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EA%20day%20after%20Shah%20alleged%20that%20the%20survey%20report%20has%20inflated%20the%20number%20of%20the%20Yadavs%20and%20Muslims%20at%20the%20cost%20of%20the%20EBCs%2C%20the%20JD(U)%20came%20out%20with%20a%20graphic%20on%20social%20media.%20It%20showed%20the%20Nitish%20Kumar%20government%20paying%20Rs%2050%2C000%20and%20Rs%201%2C%2000%2C000%20to%20the%20youths%20of%20the%20OBCs%20and%20EBCs%20as%20%E2%80%9Cencouragement%20amount%E2%80%9D%20as%20they%20sit%20for%20the%20Bihar%20Public%20Service%20Commission%20and%20Union%20Public%20Service%20Commission%20examinations%20respectively.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Nitish%20government%20also%20gave%20appointment%20letters%20to%20over%201.20%20lakh%20teachers%20in%20adherence%20to%20its%20reservation%20policy%20for%20EBCs%2C%20OBCs%2C%20Scheduled%20Castes%20(STs)%2C%20Scheduled%20Tribes%20(STs)%20and%20women.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Ffull-text-bihar-caste-survey-highlights-marginalised-micro-communities-bjp-faces-electoral-dilemma%5C%22%3EBihar%20Caste%20Survey%20Highlights%20Marginalised%20Micro-Communities%3B%20BJP%20Faces%20Electoral%20Dilemma%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EReligion%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EApart%20from%20levelling%20the%20allegation%20of%20%E2%80%98appeasement%E2%80%99%20against%20the%20Nitish%20government%2C%20Shah%20appealed%20to%20the%20people%20of%20Bihar%20to%20%E2%80%9Cjoin%20the%20nation%E2%80%9D%20in%20participating%20in%20the%20%3Cem%3Eaarti%3C%2Fem%3E%20rituals%20at%20the%20%3Cem%3Epranprartishtha%3C%2Fem%3E%20(infusing%20life)%20ceremony%20in%20the%20Ram%20temple%20of%20Ayodhya.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20talked%20about%20Sanatan%20Dharma%20and%20the%20upcoming%20Chhath%20festival%20%E2%80%93%20the%20most%20popular%20festival%20of%20the%20state.%20Observers%2C%20however%2C%20interpreted%20Shah%E2%80%99s%20speech%20at%20Muzaffarpur%20more%20as%20an%20effort%20to%20rope%20in%20Bihar%E2%80%99s%20EBCs%20in%20the%20same%20manner%20as%20BJP%20has%20done%20in%20neighbouring%20Uttar%20Pradesh.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20easy%20to%20see%20how%20the%20public%20reception%20to%20the%20caste%20survey%20report%20followed%20by%20the%20job%20event%20in%20the%20state%20on%20November%202%20led%20BJP%20and%20Shah%20to%20amp%20up%20attention%20on%20Bihar.%C2%A0Shah%20took%20time%20off%20from%20the%20elections%20in%20five%20states%20and%20addressed%20a%20rally%20at%20Muzaffarpur%20and%20announced%20that%20he%20would%20address%20rallies%20in%20all%20the%20districts%20of%20the%20state%20in%20the%20next%2013%20months%20in%20the%20run%20up%20to%20the%202024%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHe%20attacked%20the%20INDIA%20alliance%20describing%20it%20as%20the%20storehouse%20of%20family%20promotion%20and%20selfish%20elements.%20%E2%80%9CWhile%20one%20leader%20is%20working%20to%20make%20his%20son%20a%20CM%2C%20another%20is%20dreaming%20to%20become%20PM.%20They%20won%E2%80%99t%20succeed%20and%20Narendra%20Modi%20will%20win%20again%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said%2C%20referring%20to%20Lalu%20Prasad%20Yadav%20and%20Nitish%20Kumar.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EUnease%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EDespite%20Amit%20Shah%E2%80%99s%20efforts%20the%20BJP%20does%20not%20seem%20to%20be%20making%20much%20headway%20in%20Bihar%20where%20INDIA%20alliance%20appears%20to%20be%20on%20its%20strongest%20wicket%2C%20thanks%20to%20Nitish%20and%20his%20deputy%20Tejashwi.%20But%20not%20all%20is%20well.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20at%20a%20Communist%20Party%20of%20India%20(CPI)%20rally%20at%20Patna%20on%20November%202%2C%20Nitish%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20Congress%20is%20too%20preoccupied%20with%20the%20assembly%20elections%20in%20five%20states%20and%20is%20not%20paying%20much%20attention%20towards%20the%20Indian%20National%20Developmental%20Inclusive%20Alliance%20(INDIA)%E2%80%9D%20indicating%20his%20unhappiness%20with%20the%20grand%20old%20party.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ENitish%E2%80%99s%20remark%20preceded%20the%20Samajwadi%20Party%20chief%20Akhilesh%20Yadav%20attacking%20the%20Congress%20for%20not%20accommodating%20his%20party%20in%20Madhya%20Pradesh.%20The%20SP%20was%20said%20to%20have%20wanted%20the%20Congress%20to%20spare%20about%20six%20to%20seven%20seats%20for%20it%20in%20the%20MP.%20The%20JD(U)%20too%20has%20fielded%2040%20candidates%20in%20Madhya%20Pradesh.%20The%20party%E2%80%99s%20secretary%20general%20K.C.%20Tyagi%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20up%20to%20the%20Congress%20to%20accommodate%20us%E2%80%9D.%20His%20statement%20indicated%20that%20the%20party%20too%20wanted%20its%20share%20in%20the%20seats%20in%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20differences%20between%20the%20Congress%20which%20is%20the%20prime%20player%20against%20the%20BJP%20in%20Madhya%20Pradesh%2C%20Chhattisgarh%20and%20Rajasthan%20and%20the%20regional%20parties%20are%20said%20to%20be%20rooted%20more%20in%20the%20desire%20of%20the%20regional%20parties%20to%20expand%20themselves%20beyond%20their%20states%20than%20the%20ideology%20and%20the%20larger%20goal%20to%20defeat%20the%20BJP%20in%202024.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAt%20the%20level%20of%20the%20issues%20and%20commitment%20to%20drive%20the%20BJP%20out%2C%20the%20Congress%20and%20other%20INDIA%20partners%20are%20on%20the%20same%20page.%20We%20will%20fight%20together%20against%20the%20Hindutva%20party%20on%20the%20issues%20of%20saving%20democracy%20and%20constitution%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20Bihar%20Congress%20president%2C%20Akhilesh%20Singh%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fauthor%2Fnalin-verma%5C%22%20data-saferedirecturl%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Furl%3Fq%3Dhttp%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fauthor%2Fnalin-verma%26amp%3Bsource%3Dgmail%26amp%3Bust%3D1699411021273000%26amp%3Busg%3DAOvVaw2RPjl4T7i87lfzpTj1m-2q%5C%22%3ENalin%C2%A0Verma%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0is%20a%20senior%20journalist%2C%20author%2C%20media%20educator%20and%20independent%20researcher%20in%20folklore.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1699340427000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F07122711%2FUntitled-design-8.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Famit-shah-bihar-caste-survey-yadav-muslim%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22It%20is%20easy%20to%20see%20how%20the%20public%20reception%20to%20the%20caste%20survey%20report%20followed%20by%20the%20job%20event%20in%20the%20state%20on%20November%202%20led%20BJP%20and%20Shah%20to%20amp%20up%20attention%20on%20Bihar.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A7%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Famit-shah-bihar-caste-survey-yadav-muslim%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Agastya%20fuels%20dating%20rumours%20as%20he%20escorts%20Suhana%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1699340256000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-105030774%2Cimgsize-29730.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fagastya-nanda-fuels-dating-rumours-as-he-escorts-suhana-khan-to-her-car-after-diwali-party-watch%2Farticleshow%2F105030830.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C