icleshow%2F105030900.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F105030900.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3ESouth%20Korean%20group%20DKB%20is%20set%20to%20make%20a%20comeback%20on%20November%2030%20with%20eight%20members%2C%20following%20the%20departure%20of%20Theo.%20Brave%20Entertainment%20confirmed%20the%20news%20and%20revealed%20that%20the%20group%20will%20release%20a%20new%20mini%20album%2C%20showcasing%20their%20%26quot%3Bhigh%20performance%26quot%3B%20style.%20DKB%20is%20currently%20shooting%20a%20music%20video%20in%20Los%20Angeles%2C%20indicating%20their%20expansion%20of%20creative%20horizons.%20Profile%20photos%20of%20the%20eight%20members%20were%20unveiled%2C%20excluding%20Theo%20who%20left%20due%20to%20a%20drunk%20driving%20controversy.%20DKB's%20return%20comes%20three%20months%20after%20their%20last%20album%2C%20and%20fans%20are%20eagerly%20awaiting%20their%20comeback.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fk-pop%2Fdkb-announces-grand-comeback-on-november-30-with-eight-member-lineup-after-theos-departure%2Farticleshow%2F105030900.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Watch%3A%20Empty%20Bouquet%20For%20Priyanka%20Gandhi%20Leads%20To%20'LOL'%20Moment%20On%20Stage%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIn%20some%20comic%20relief%20amid%20a%20hectic%20poll%20campaign%2C%20Congress%20leader%20Priyanka%20Gandhi%20Vadra%20was%20left%20amused%20when%20a%20party%20leader%20presented%20her%20with%20a%20bouquet%20with%20the%20flowers%20missing.%20Yes%2C%20you%20read%20it%20right.%20The%20Congress%20leader%20could%20not%20suppress%20a%20laugh%20when%20she%20noticed%20that%20the%20neat%20wrap%20handed%20to%20her%20was%20actually%20empty.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20hilarious%20moments%20were%20caught%20on%20camera%20yesterday%20during%20the%20Congress%20leader's%20rally%20at%20Indore%20in%20Madhya%20Pradesh%2C%20which%20votes%20on%20November%2017.%20The%20Congress%20is%20pushing%20hard%20for%20a%20victory%20in%20the%20state%2C%20where%20it%20formed%20a%20government%20last%20time%20but%20lost%20power%20after%20a%20rebellion%20led%20by%20Jyotiraditya%20Scindia%2C%20now%20with%20the%20BJP.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20rally%20was%20aired%20live%20on%20social%20media%20handles%20of%20the%20Congress.%20Sharing%20the%20link%2C%20Ms%20Gandhi%20Vadra%20posted%20on%20X%2C%20%26quot%3BIndore%20is%20the%20land%20of%20Maharani%20Ahilyabai%20Holkar%20which%20is%20known%20for%20justice%2C%20truth%20and%20good%20governance.%20The%20people%20here%20will%20restore%20those%20values%20by%20finishing%20off%20corruption%20and%20bad%20governance.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAhilyabai%20Holkar%20was%20a%20Maratha%20queen%20in%20the%2018th%20century%20who%20ruled%20over%20Indore%20for%20nearly%20three%20decades.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20video%20of%20the%20poll%20meeting%20shows%20Ms%20Gandhi%20Vadra%20being%20welcomed%20by%20Congress%20leaders.%20One%20by%20one%2C%20party%20leaders%20walk%20to%20her%20and%20greet%20her.%20The%20Congress%20leader%20is%20seen%20smiling%20and%20greeting%20them%20back.%20Some%20leaders%20gift%20her%20roses%2C%20others%20pose%20for%20photographs%20with%20the%20top%20leader.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAt%20this%20point%2C%20a%20man%20walks%20into%20the%20frame%20holding%20what%20looks%20like%20a%20bouquet.%20He%20hands%20it%20over%20to%20Ms%20Gandhi%20Vadra%20and%20she%20starts%20laughing%20as%20soon%20as%20she%20looks%20at%20it.%20She%20then%20points%20to%20the%20empty%20wrap%20as%20if%20to%20ask%20where%20the%20flowers%20are.%20The%20party%20workers%2C%20visibly%20embarassed%2C%20mumbles%20something.%20Ms%20Gandhi%20Vadra%20can't%20stop%20laughing%20as%20others%20on%20the%20stage%20join%20in.%20The%20man%20disappears%20as%20soon%20as%20he%20had%20come.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20comic%20relief%