ags%20in%20bright%20shades%20of%20orange%2C%20blue%2C%20green%20and%20white%20hang%20from%20mud%20houses%20and%20trees%2C%20amidst%20great%20tracts%20of%20farmed%20land.%20The%20Bastar%20region%2C%20with%2012%20seats%2C%20goes%20to%20election%20today%2C%20November%207%20along%20with%20eight%20other%20constituencies%20in%20two%20other%20districts.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EIn%202018%2C%20Congress%20had%20won%2011%20out%20of%20the%2012%20seats%2C%20and%20had%20reclaimed%20the%20lost%20seat%20in%20the%20by-polls%20necessitated%20after%20the%20election%20due%20to%20the%20death%20of%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20leader%20and%20winner%20Bheema%20Mandavi.%20After%2015%20years%20in%20power%2C%20the%20BJP%20had%20lost%20the%20entire%20region%2C%20with%20people%20simmering%20against%20the%20party%E2%80%99s%20leaders%20and%20politics.%20The%20tribal%20vote%20had%20counted%20the%20highest%20in%20the%20anti-BJP%20sentiment%2C%20with%20issues%20like%20violence%20against%20tribals%20in%20the%20garb%20of%20anti-Maoist%20strategy%20and%20heavy%20fortification%20of%20the%20region%20using%20security%20camps%20among%20other%20discrimination%20taking%20centrestage.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fchhattisgarh-maoist-dantewada-development%5C%22%3EChhattisgarh%3A%20In%20Dantewada%2C%20Maoist%20Threats%20Have%20Receded%20But%20Development%20Hasn%E2%80%99t%20Come%20in%20Either%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EDespite%20the%20advantage%2C%20the%20ruling%20Congress%20has%20had%20to%20change%20their%20candidates%20in%20five%20out%20of%20the%2012%20seats.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20324px)%2085vw%2C%20324px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F07095441%2FScreenshot-2023-11-07-at-9.54.35%25E2%2580%25AFAM.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22324%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F07095441%2FScreenshot-2023-11-07-at-9.54.35%25E2%2580%25AFAM.png%20510w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F07095441%2FScreenshot-2023-11-07-at-9.54.35%25E2%2580%25AFAM-224x300.png%20224w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-683816%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22435%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EChhavindra%20Karma.%20Photo%3A%20Official%20Instagram.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EThe%20Congress%20has%20fielded%20Chhavindra%20Karma%2C%20son%20of%20present%20MLA%20Devati%20Karma%20from%20Dantewada%20constituency.%20In%20Dantewada%2C%20Devati%20Karma%20became%20the%20MLA%20after%20Bheema%20Mandavi%E2%80%99s%20death%20in%202018.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EIn%202023%2C%20the%20BJP%20gave%20their%20ticket%20to%20Chaitram%20Atami%2C%20a%20resident%20of%20Hirenar%2C%20known%20among%20the%20rural%20population%20as%20%E2%80%9Cone%20of%20them%E2%80%9D.%20Atami%20was%20a%20prominent%20Judum%20leader%20(leader%20of%20Salwa%20Judum%2C%20a%20people%E2%80%99s%20militia%20movement%20against%20Maoists%20started%20by%20late%20Mahendra%20Karma)%20with%20several%20threats%20from%20the%20Maoists%20to%20his%20credit.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3E%E2%80%9CBefore%20the%20Congress%20declared%20their%20candidate%2C%20we%20all%20believed%20Atami%20would%20win.%20But%2C%20now%20with%20Chhavindra%20contesting%20the%20election%2C%20it%20will%20be%20a%20tough%20fight%2C%E2%80%9D%20a%20villager%20from%20Gidam%20%3Cem%3Etehsil%3C%2Fem%3E%20said.%20In%20Dantewada%2C%20Chhavindra%20Karma%20has%20the%20advantage%20of%20various%20factors%20working%20in%20his%20favour%2C%20including%20sympathy%20of%20being%20a%20Karma%20family%20scion%20who%20is%20taking%20his%20late%20father%E2%80%99s%20legacy%20forward.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EKondagaon%2C%20where%20the%20Congress%20had%20won%20with%20a%2