politics%2Fanti-bjp-anti-congress-where-the-tussle-lies-in-bastar%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22'In%20Bastar%2C%20the%20government%20schemes%20are%20not%20as%20pertinent%20as%20they%20are%20in%20the%20plains%2C'%20as%20a%20political%20worker%20puts%20it.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fanti-bjp-anti-congress-where-the-tussle-lies-in-bastar%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%2235%20elephants%20suddenly%20dropped%20dead%20in%202020.%20Their%20case%20has%20finally%20been%20solved.%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225100%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Silhouette%20of%20elephant%20in%20tall%20grass%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F654993f13cc84b4dfafd754f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223400%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EJeremy%20Woodhouse%2FGetty%20images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EIn%202020%2C%2035%20elephants%20dropped%20dead%20in%20Zimbabwe%20over%20a%20month%20timespan.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThere%20were%20no%20signs%20of%20external%20trauma%20or%20intentional%20poisoning.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ENow%2C%20scientists%20said%20they%20believe%20they%20have%20the%20answer.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20took%20a%20team%20of%20scientists%20nearly%20three%20years%20to%20figure%20out%20what%20caused%20a%20mass%20die-off%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fphotos-390-botswana-elephants-found-inexplicably-dead-near-water-2020-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Eelephants%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20Zimbabwe%2C%20but%20they%20finally%20closed%20the%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBetween%20August%20and%20September%202020%2C%2035%20elephant%20carcasses%20were%20retrieved%20from%20various%20safaris%20and%20protected%20lands%20in%20Zimbabwe%20%E2%80%94%20with%20eleven%20of%20these%20animals%20dying%20within%20a%2024-hour%20period.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20team%20responsible%20for%20figuring%20out%20what%20happened%20initially%20ruled%20out%20intentional%20poisoning%2C%20poaching%2C%20and%20drought%20conditions%2C%20per%20the%20study%20published%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%3Fh%3D8f1d89bb567873c81608109dae97a0c9cf6673815b4059f27e0b1554351c5d39%26postID%3D65499271fe456b34e607d06e%26postSlug%3Dscientists-solve-mystery-of-35-dead-elephants-2023-11%26site%3Dbi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.nature.com%252Farticles%252Fs41467-023-41987-z%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3ENature%20Communications%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%20There%20didn't%20seem%20to%20be%20any%20signs%20of%20external%20trauma%20on%20the%20elephants.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThey%20then%20decided%20to%20look%20inside%20and%20sample%20the%20brain%2C%20liver%2C%20and%20spleen%20tissue%20from%2015%20elephants%20and%20confirmed%20that%20six%20elephants%20had%20bacteria%20known%20as%20Bisgaard%20taxon%2045%20in%20their%20system.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThey%20concluded%20that%20most%2C%20if%20not%20all%2C%20the%20elephants%20died%20as%20a%20result%20of%20septicemia%2C%20or%20blood%20poisoning%2C%20caused%20by%20the%20bacteria.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAlthough%20there%20was%20not%20culture%20or%20molecular%20evidence%20to%20confirm%20Bisgaard%20taxon%2045%20in%20more%20than%20six%20mortalities%20in%20Zimbabwe%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20study%20said%2C%20%26quot%3Bthe%20elephants%20examined%20were%20in%20good%20body%20condition%20and%20unlikely%20to%20have%20died%20of%20drought-related%20starvation%20or%20severe%20dehydration%20alone.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20bacteria%20is%20not%20known%20to%20kill%20African%20elephants%2C%20scientists%20said%2C%20but%20they%20are%20beginning%20to%20see%20a%20potential%20pattern%20of%20cases%20like%20this%20in%20herds%20across%20Africa.%20There%20have%20also%20been%20cases%20of%20blood%20infections%20killing%20off%20elephant%20populations%20in%20Asia.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20study%20authors%20said%20they%20are%20still%20stumped%20as%20to%20how%20the%20bacteria%20was%20transmitted%20to%20the%20elephant%20populations.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20authors%20write%20that%20climate%20change-induced%20factors%20like%20heat%2C%20drought%2C%20and%20population%20density%20could%20make%20this%20type%20of%20bacteria%20transmission%20more%20common.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20premature%20to%20say%20that%20climate%20change%20has%20influenced%20(this)%20but%20it%20may%20do%20so%20in%20future%20if%20we%20get%20more%20and%20prolonged%20droughts%2C%20or%20the%20rainfall%20patterns%20(change)%20and%20we%20have%20a%20much%20harsher%20dry%20season%2C%26quot%3B%20Dr.%20Chris%20Foggin%2C%20one%20of%20the%20study's%20co-authors%20and%20a%20veterinarian%20at%20Victoria%20Falls%20Wildlife%20Trust%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnn.com%2F2023%2F11%2F06%2Fafrica%2Fafrican-elephant-deaths-zimbabwe-scn%2Findex.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Etold%20CNN.%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20%26quot%3BI%20do%20think%20that%20if%20that%20is%20the%20case%2C%20then%20we%20are%20more%20likely%20to%20see%20this%20sort%20of%20mortality%20event%20occurring%20again.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%2035%20deaths%20in%20Zimbabwe%20also%20coincided%20with%20a%20mass%20die-off%20of%20elephants%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbotswana-stalling-on-investigation-into-mass-elephant-death-2020-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3EBotswana%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%202020.%20At%20least%20350%20elephants%20died%20within%20a%20three-month%20timespan%2C%20and%20researchers%20at%20the%20time%20concluded%20that%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmass-elephant-die-off-bostwana-toxic-algae-2020-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Eblue-green%20algae%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20contaminated%20local%20water%20sources%20and%20poisoned%20the%20elephants.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFoggin%20told%20CNN%2