n.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.huffpost.com%2Fentry%2Fwework-bankruptcy-filing_n_6549b5bee4b0e63c9dc0a073%2Famp%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.huffpost.com%2Fentry%2Fwework-bankruptcy-filing_n_6549b5bee4b0e63c9dc0a073%2Famp%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Bad%20Kharif%2C%20Worse%20Monsoon%3A%20Inside%20India%E2%80%99s%20Food%20Security%20Doubts%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F07092550%2F6119486736_434f1d90d0_c.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3ENovember%20brings%20doubts%20about%20the%20fate%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20food%20security.%20Compare%20kharif%20production%20estimates%20for%202023-2024%20with%20the%20deficit%20monsoon%20report%20for%20kharif%2C%20and%20match%20them%20with%20hyperinflation%20in%20food%2C%20price%20volatility%20and%20erratic%20rains%2C%20and%20something%20does%20smell%20fishy.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOnce%20we%20read%20them%20together%2C%20one%20of%20them%20don%E2%80%99t%20seem%20to%20make%20sense%2C%20because%20India%20is%20largely%20a%20rain-fed%20agrarian%20system%20and%20a%20bad%20monsoon%20with%20extreme%20erratic%20rain%20events%20has%20a%20very%20high%20probability%20of%20dampening%20agricultural%20production%2C%20yet%20the%20crop%20estimates%20that%20paddy%20production%20dipped%20only%203.79%25%20despite%20increased%20area%20under%20paddy%20cultivation.%20So%20the%20figures%20seem%20to%20be%20leading%20the%20reader%20astray.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBut%20before%20diving%20into%20crop%20production%2C%20let%20us%20look%20at%20the%20monsoon.%20India%20is%20under%20the%20El%20Ni%C3%B1o%20spell%2C%20which%20correctly%20points%20to%20irregular%20monsoon%20and%20probable%20drought-like%20situations.%20It%20was%20no%20surprise%20that%20August%20was%20almost%20drought-like%2C%20as%20cyclone%20Biparjoy%20showered%20excessive%20rainfall%20on%20western%20India%2C%20right%20before%20our%20traditional%20monsoon%20began.%20Then%20came%20a%20drought-like%20August%2C%20reporting%20the%20lowest%20rainfall%20in%20decades.%20September%20brought%20a%20little%20relief%2C%20but%20October%20again%20exacerbated%20the%20problems%20of%20farmers%2C%20especially%20in%20rain-fed%20areas.%20From%20Telangana%20to%20Kerala%2C%20the%20south%20experienced%20heavy%20rainfall%20deficits.%20Kerala%20had%20a%20deficit%20of%2034%25.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAlong%20with%20the%20drought-like%20months%2C%202023%20also%20witnessed%202%2C321%20heavy%20rainfall%20events%2C%20with%20precipitation%20of%2011.5-20.5%20cm%20in%2024%20hours.%20The%20devastation%20caused%20by%20these%20events%20brought%20farming%20and%20even%20life%20to%20a%20standstill%20in%20many%20parts%20of%20the%20country.%20Areas%20of%20Himachal%20and%20Punjab%20are%20still%20reeling%20from%20flood%20and%20rain%20damage.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EApart%20from%20these%2C%20there%20were%20also%20421%20extremely%20heavy%20rain%20events%2C%20with%20precipitation%20over%2020.5%20cm%20in%2024%20hours%2C%20in%202023.%20Now%2C%20the%20IMD%20and%20the%20government%20are%20consulting%20their%20rain%20gauges%20and%20trying%20to%20say%20that%20it%20was%20a%20near-normal%20monsoon%2C%20but%20this%20is%20very%20far%20from%20the%20truth.%20The%20monthly%20average%20of%20rain%20could%20hide%20important%20agrarian%20gaps%20and%20can%E2%80%99t%20be%20trusted%2C%20especially%20for%20understanding%20agriculture.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fagriculture%2Ffood-security-green-revolution%5C%22%3EIndia%E2%80%99s%20Food%20Security%20Is%20Thanks%20to%20the%20Green%20Revolution.%20Let%20Us%20Not%20Deny%20It%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAll%20over%20India%2C%20farmers%20reported%20floods%20and%20drought-like%20conditions%2C%20especially%20when%20it%20was%20time%20to%20irrigate%20the%20kharif%20crops.%20After%20an%20early%20sowing%20due%20to%20government%20advisories%20and%20cyclone%20Biporjoy%2C%20kharif%20fields%20were%20left%20dry%20in%20August%2C%20putting%20a%20biotic%20stress%20on%20the%20crops.%20Farmers%20without%20irrigation%20suffered%20during%20this%20period.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20most%20agrarian%20clusters%2C%20erratic%20rains%20broke%20routine%20crop-growing%20cycles%20and%20untimely%20excessive%20moisture%20when%20it%20rained%20promoted%20the%20emergence%20of%20new%20pests%20and%20plant%20diseases%2C%20which%20farmers%20did%20not%20anticipate.%20The%20crisis%20in%20the%20supply%20of%20tomatoes%20and%20vegetables%20in%20early%20July-August%20bore%20testimony%20to%20this%20disruption.%20Rabi%20sowing%20is%20also%20being%20impacted%20as%20the%20retreating%20monsoon%20failed%20to%20get%20water%20to%20rain-fed%20areas.%20This%20problem%20is%20only%20increasing%20and%20we%20may%20be%20looking%20at%20a%20reprise%20of%202019%2C%20which%20featured%20extreme%20rainfall%20damage.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20let%E2%80%99s%20talk%20about%20food%20production.%20Keep%20in%20mind%20that%20kharif%20production%20and%20rain%20are%20deeply%20connected.%20Alarm%20bells%20started%20to%20go%20off%20in%20September%2C%20when%20the%20US%20Department%20of%20Agriculture%20predicted%20that%20Indian%20rice%20production%20would%20fall%20by%203%25%20this%20kharif.%20Experts%20and%20the%20government%20brushed%20it%20off%20but%20recently%2C%20the%20government%20released%20kharif%20crop%20estimates%20and%20admitted%20that%20paddy%20production%20has%20fallen%20by%203.76%25%20despite%20an%20increase%20in%20acreage.%20The%20government%20also%20stated%20that%20the%20%E2%80%9Ctotal%20kharif%20pulses%20production%20for%202023-24%20is%20estimated%20to%20be%20lower%20than%20previous%20year%20due%20to%20climatic%20conditions.%20Total%20kharif%20pulses%20production%20during%202023-24%20is%20estimated%20at%2071.18.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESo%2C%20apart%20from%20rice%2C%20lentils%20are%20also%20squeezed.%20When%20we%20look%20at%20other%20food%20crops%20or%20cattle%20fodder%2C%20kharif%20has%20under-performed.%20Repeated%20spells%20of%20hyperinflation%20in%20vegetables%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20point%20to%20a%20regular%20kharif%20production%20cycle%2C%20either.%20The%20monsoon%20report%20also%20signals%20that%2C%20yet%20the%20crop%20production%20figures%20don%E2%80%99t%20correspond%20to%20the%20monsoon%20damages.%20If%20all%20the%20other%20signs%20are%20true%2C%20the%20crop%20production%20should%20be%20much%20lower%20than%20expected.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cblockquote%3E%3Cp%3ESo%20if%20we%20compare%20IMD%E2%80%99s%20monsoon%20report%20and%20the%20agriculture%20ministry%20crop%20estimates%2C%20they%20don%E2%80%99t%20point%20to%20the%20same%20conclusions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20question%20is%2C%20which%20one%20is%20more%20correct.%20If%20the%20monsoon%20data%20is%20correct%2C%20crop%20losses%20should%20be%20higher%2C%20and%20if%20the%20crop%20estimates%20are%20correct%20monsoon%20figures%20should%20have%20been%20much%20better.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20government%20wants%20to%20reduce%20public%20panic%20or%20another%20spell%20of%20food%20inflation%20and%20hoarding%2C%20and%20remains%20ambiguous%20on%20the%20real%20food%20situation%20while%20silently%20moving%20to%20implement%20stricter%20controls%20through%20import%20restrictions%2C%20close%20monitoring%20of%20food%20stocks%20and%20price%20controls%2C%20etc%20to%20check%20a%20food%20crisis%20before%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20recently%20released%20Global%20Hunger%20Index%202023%20puts%20India%20at%20the%20111th%20spot%20among%20125%20countries.%20For%20a%20couple%20of%20years%2C%20it%20has%20pointed%20to%20a%20steady%20deterioration%20of%20food%20security%20in%20India.%20Now%20with%20a%20bad%20kharif%20and%20uncertain%20rabi%2C%20Indians%20need%20to%20brace%20for%20more%20food%20troubles%20ahead.%20What%20is%20needed%20is%20transparency%20on%20food%20and%20weather%20data%20and%20stricter%20control%20on%20agri-processors%20and%20food%20warehouses%2C%20so%20that%20India%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20get%20trapped%20in%20a%20food%20speculation%20trap%20again.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Ce