risis%2C%20unemployment%2C%20inflation%2C%20and%20poor%20public%20health%20and%20education%20infrastructure.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EDominance%20of%20agrarian%20issues%20in%20the%20upcoming%20polls%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fchhattisgarh-in-chandameta-with-electricity-roads-and-water-a-polling-booth-for-the-first-time%5C%22%3EChhattisgarh%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Frajasthan-congress-madhya-pradesh-chhattisgarh%5C%22%3ERajasthan%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20where%20Bhupesh%20Baghel%20and%20Ashok%20Gehlot%20are%20seeking%20another%20term%2C%20Congress%20has%20anchored%20its%20campaign%20around%20support%20to%20farmers%20and%20social%20security%20measures.%20If%20Baghel%20has%20advertised%20his%20government%20as%20one%20that%20gives%20the%20best%20minimum%20support%20price%20to%20farmers%20for%20their%20crop%2C%20Gehlot%20has%20been%20talking%20about%20measures%20like%20%E2%80%98Chiranjeevi%E2%80%99%20which%20supports%20health%20care%20up%20to%20Rs%2025%20lakh%2C%20subsidy%20on%20LPG%20cylinders%2C%20and%20the%20implementation%20of%20the%20Old%20Pension%20Scheme%20for%20retired%20government%20employees.%20Baghel%20has%20gone%20ahead%20and%20promised%20even%20better%20MSP%20rates%2C%20loan%20waivers%20for%20farmers%20and%20self-help%20groups%2C%20and%20financial%20support%20to%20school%20and%20college-going%20children.%20Gehlot%2C%20too%2C%20has%20promised%20similar%20schemes%20like%20unemployment%20allowance%2C%20better%20wage%20rates%2C%20education%20and%20health%20infrastructure.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20stories%20of%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20and%20Telangana%20are%20also%20similar.%20Congress%20has%20led%20an%20aggressive%20campaign%20by%20promising%20several%20benefits%20to%20the%20poor%2C%20and%20has%20attempted%20to%20gain%20traction%20by%20amplifying%20the%20prevailing%20anti-incumbency%20sentiment%20against%20BJP%E2%