%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EMatthew%20Tay%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E%2C%20an%20operations%20supervisor%20in%20Singapore%20for%20Tower%20Transit%2C%20a%20local%20bus%20company.%20This%20essay%20has%20been%20edited%20for%20length%20and%20clarity.%20Insider%20verified%20his%20educational%20background%2C%20college%20acceptance%20letters%2C%20and%20employment%20details.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20grew%20up%20in%20Hougang%2C%20a%20neighborhood%20in%20northeast%20Singapore%2C%20near%20a%20now%20defunct%20bus%20interchange.%20When%20I%20was%20a%20kid%2C%20my%20parents%20took%20me%20around%20a%20lot%20to%20different%20bus%20interchanges%2C%20and%20it%20sparked%20my%20interest%20in%20collecting%20brochures%20about%20buses%20and%20drawing%20the%20vehicles.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20was%20older%2C%20I%20joined%20a%20400-member%20Facebook%20group%20called%20%26quot%3BSingapore%20bus%20enthusiasts.%26quot%3B%20I%20remember%20being%20the%20youngest%20person%20in%20the%20group.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBack%20then%2C%20buses%20were%20like%20Pok%C3%A9mon%20%E2%80%94%20you%20could%20catch%20only%20certain%20types%20of%20vehicles%20depending%20on%20which%20part%20of%20Singapore%20you%20were%20in.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEach%20weekend%2C%20the%20group%20would%20target%20places%20to%20go%20to%20hop%20onto%20some%20of%20these%20buses.%20Like%20in%202012%2C%20the%20last%20non-air-conditioned%20buses%20were%20found%20only%20in%20the%20far-west%20industrial%20areas%20of%20Tuas%20%E2%80%94%20a%20neighborhood%20in%20western%20Singapore%20%E2%80%94%20so%20the%20group%20headed%20there%20to%20experience%20what%20it%20was%20like%20to%20ride%20on%20a%20bus%20with%20no%20air%20conditioning.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20didn't%20just%20tag%20along%20for%20bus-spotting%20trips%20but%20also%20collected%20memorabilia%20as%20I%20grew%20older.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20started%20collecting%20bus%20models%20from%20across%20the%20world%20when%20I%20was%2012%2C%20and%20I%20now%20have%20over%2030%20models%20in%20my%20collection%2C