d%20start%20looking%20for%20jobs%20in%20the%20bus%20industry.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20that's%20when%20I%20applied%20to%20Tower%20Transit%20Singapore%2C%20a%20local%20bus%20company%20that%20operates%2059%20bus%20services%20out%20of%20nine%20interchanges%20in%20Singapore%20where%20I%20now%20work%20as%20an%20operations%20supervisor.%20I%20joined%20the%20team%20in%20August%202022%2C%20and%20I%20help%20keep%20our%20facilities%20working%20and%20our%20buses%20on%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThough%20it%20has%20been%20a%20dream%20job%20for%20me%2C%20my%20decision%20to%20skip%20college%20was%20shocking%20to%20some.%20That's%20because%20I%20was%20accepted%20into%20Singapore's%20top%20three%20universities%20%E2%80%94%20the%20National%20University%20of%20Singapore%2C%20the%20Nanyang%20Technological%20University%2C%20and%20the%20Singapore%20Management%20University%20%E2%80%94%20to%20get%20a%20bachelor's%20degree%20in%20business%2C%20information%20systems%2C%20or%20public%20policy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20classmates%20were%20surprised%20%E2%80%94%20they%20all%20expected%20me%20to%20attend%20college%20because%20of%20how%20well%20I%20scored.%20I%20was%20a%20straight-A%20student%2C%20and%20my%20GPA%20in%20polytechnic%2C%20or%20Singapore's%20equivalent%20to%20a%20vocational%20high%20school%2C%20was%20a%20nearly%20perfect%203.99%20out%20of%204.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20my%20lecturers%20found%20out%2C%20they%20even%20messaged%20me%20saying%20a%20university%20degree%20was%20something%20I%20should%20seriously%20consider%20in%20the%20future%2C%20if%20not%20then.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3ENow%20I'm%20the%20behind-the-scenes%20guy%20who%20keeps%20things%20running%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20an%20operations%20supervisor%2C%20I%20work%20in%20shifts.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20start%20the%20morning%20shift%20at%205%20by%20checking%20our%20facilities%20to%20make%20sure%20they're%20working%20fine%2C%20setting%20up%20our%20passenger%20service%20office%2C%20making%20sure%20the%20first%20buses%20depart%20on%20time%2C%20and%20coordi