th%26quot%3B%20to%20support%20their%20allies%20in%20wartime.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere's%20seven%20days%20in%20a%20week%2C%2024%20hours%20in%20a%20day%2C%20and%20only%20so%20much%20time%20and%20attention%20that%20people%20like%20Biden%20can%20devote%20to%20different%20problems%2C%26quot%3B%20Walt%20told%20Insider.%20%26quot%3BSo%20if%20you%20have%20to%20focus%20a%20lot%20of%20attention%20on%20the%20Middle%20East%2C%20not%20just%20during%20the%20conflict%20but%20probably%20for%20years%20afterward%2C%20that%20just%20means%20less%20time%20for%20other%20problems%2C%20and%20other%20countries%20are%20going%20to%20feel%20neglected.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20Ukraine%2C%20that%20sense%20of%20neglect%20may%20come%20in%20the%20form%20of%20munitions%20shortages.%20The%20US%20and%20its%20allies%20have%20already%20begun%20struggling%20to%20keep%20up%20the%20supply%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpentagon-increasing-production-of-155mm-artillery-shells-2023-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E155mm%20artillery%20shells%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20are%20a%20key%20part%20of%20a%20war%20of%20attrition%20like%20this%20one%20has%20become%2C%20where%20one%20side%20tries%20to%20wear%20the%20other%20down%20in%20a%20steady%20barrage%20of%20attacks%20over%20a%20long%20period.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThough%20the%20US%20has%20plans%20to%20ramp%20up%20production%20of%20155mm%20artillery%20by%20500%25%20over%20the%20next%20two%20years%2C%20the%20country%20currently%20produces%20just%20over%2014%2C000%20rounds%20a%20month%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpentagon-increasing-production-of-155mm-artillery-shells-2023-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EInsider%20previously%20reported%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0which%20Ukrainian%20troops%20can%20blow%20through%20in%20about%20two%20days.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNow%20that%20we're%20going%20to%20be%20helping%20rearm%20Israel%2C%20some%20of%20the%20things%20that%20might%20hav