CValorant%2C%E2%80%9D%20which%20is%20displaying%20the%20Agent%20page%20for%20the%20character%20Fade.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65454b9a36d588dc55cab98c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20screen%20is%20fast%2C%20crisp%2C%20and%20wonderfully%20vibrant.%3Cp%3EMichael%20Chan%20and%20Paige%20Clarke%2FInsider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3EAdd%20in%20a%20peak%20brightness%20of%201%2C000%20nits%20for%20the%20dual-mode%20display%20or%20500%20nits%20for%20the%20QHD%20version%20%E2%80%94%20both%20incredibly%20rare%20among%20gaming%20laptops%20%E2%80%94%20and%20you%20have%20a%20supremely%20high-quality%20display.%20I%20keep%20the%20brightness%20of%20all%20my%20devices%20maxed%20out%20at%20all%20times%2C%20and%20even%20I%20occasionally%20had%20to%20turn%20down%20the%20Blade%2016's%20brightness%20to%20protect%20my%20eyes.%3Cp%3ERazer%20prides%20itself%20on%20aesthetics.%20And%20in%20that%20department%2C%20the%20Blade%2016%20excels.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Performance%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20laptop's%20high-end%20hardware%20performs%20well%20%E2%80%94%20but%20the%20CPU%20has%20issues%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222004%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Someone%20using%20a%20Razer%20Blade%2016%20laptop%20while%20it%20sits%20against%20a%20green%20background.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65454c27b788914e55503169%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221332%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EEvery%20Blade%2016%20model%20comes%20with%20new%20and%20powerful%20hardware%20by%20Intel%20and%20Nvidia.%3Cp%3EMichael%20Chan%20and%20Paige%20Clarke%2FInsider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3EWhen%20it%20comes%20to%20hardware%20and%20performance%2C%20the%20Blade%2016%20earns%20its%20premium%20status.%20Mostly.%3Cp%3EIts%20four%20primary%20configurations%20are%20differentiated%20by%20their%20graphics%20cards%2C%20which%20range%20from%20an%20Nvidia%20RTX%204060%20all%20the%20way%20up%20to%20a%204090.%20My%20review%20unit%2C%20which%20features%20an%20RTX%204070%2C%20performed%20incredibly%20well%20across%20the%20board%2C%20in%20FHD%2C%20QHD%20(through%20an%20external%20monitor)%2C%20and%204K%20resolutions.%20Popular%20but%20low-effort%20games%20like%20Valorant%20and%20Rocket%20League%20consistently%20put%20out%20hundreds%20of%20frames%20per%20second%20(FPS)%2C%20and%20higher-end%20games%20like%20Grand%20Theft%20Auto%20V%20and%20Overwatch%202%20offered%20a%20solid%2060%20FPS.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMore%20intensive%20games%20%E2%80%94%20like%20Elden%20Ring%2C%20BeamNG.drive%2C%20Marvel's%20Spider-Man%20Remastered%2C%20and%20Cyberpunk%202077%20%E2%80%94%20gave%20me%20a%20consistent%2060%20FPS%20at%20high%20settings%20as%20well%2C%20with%20regular%20dips%20when%20loading%20new%20areas.%20You%20likely%20won't%20have%20to%20turn%20down%20many%20settings%20to%20keep%20the%20frame%20rate%20consistent.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThese%2040-series%20chips%20also%20support%20Nvidia's%20AI-powered%20DLSS%20features%2C%20which%20can%20artificially%20create%20extra%20frames%20in%20supported%20games.%20Even%20in%20the%20most%20intensive%20titles%2C%20this%20worked%20smoothly%20whenever%20I%20enabled%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhere%20the%20Blade%2016%20struggles%2C%20however%2C%20is%20in%20the%20CPU%20department.%20All%20Blade%2016%20models%20use%20a%2024-core%20Intel%20Core%20i9-13950HX%20processor%2C%20which%20in%20theory%20is%20one%20of%20the%20most%20powerful%20laptop%20CPUs%20available.%20And%20to%20be%20clear%2C%20the%20laptop%20runs%20very%20well!%20During%20my%20time%20with%20the%20Blade%2016%2C%20apps%20opened%20quickly%2C%20I%20multitasked%20without%20issues%2C%20and%20intensive%20programs%20like%20Adobe%20Photoshop%20and%20Premiere%20ran%20without%20a%20hitch%2C%20even%20when%20editing%20high-res%20RAW%20image%20files.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20across%20multiple%20Geekbench%20tests%20which%20simulate%20a%20variety%20of%20CPU-intensive%20tasks%2C%20the%20Blade%2016%20scored%20equal%20to%20or%20worse%20than%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Ftech%2Fdell-g15-gaming-laptop-review%5C%22%3EDell%20G15%3C%2Fa%3E's%2014-core%20i7-13650HX.%20And%20boot-up%20times%20weren't%20nearly%20as%20fast%20as%20similar%20laptops%20%E2%80%94%20why%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20Razer%20Blade%2016%20laptop%20propped%20up%20against%20a%20green%20background.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65454d4136d588dc55cabbd6%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Blade%2016's%20Intel%20CPU%20doesn't%20always%20perform%20as%20well%20as%20it%20logically%20should.%3Cp%3EMichael%20Chan%20and%20Paige%20Clarke%2FInsider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3EThe%20culprit%20could%20be%20the%20battery.%20My%20Razer%20Blade%2016%20model%20comes%20with%20a%20280W%20charger%2C%20while%20the%20Dell%20G15%20has%20a%20330W%20charger%2C%20which%20made%20me%20suspect%20that%20the%20Blade%2016%20could%20have%20a%20weaker%20power%20supply.%20It's%20also%20much%20thinner%20than%20the%20G15%2C%20which%20usually%20suggests%20less%20power.%20This%20would%20lead%20to%20a%20bottleneck%2C%20as%20the%20Blade%2016's%20CPU%20simply%20doesn't%20have%20enough%20power%20to%20run%20at%20max%20performance.%20But%20looking%20at%20the%20specs%20for%20both%20laptops%2C%20the%20Blade%2016's%20built-in%20battery%20seems%20to%20have%20a%20higher%20voltage.%C2%A0%3Cp%3EIt%20could%20also%20be%20that%20the%20Blade%2016's%20CPU%20has%20a%20lower%20base%20frequency.%20The%20listed%20specification%20sheets%20show%20that%20there%20is%20a%20difference%2C%20but%20not%20so%20much%20that%20it%20should%20have%20this%20much%20of%20an%20impact%3A%202.20GHz%20for%20the%20Blade%2016's%20i9%2C%20and%202.60GHz%20for%20the%20G15's%20i7.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you%20want%20to%20squeeze%20the%20most%20power%20out%20of%20the%20Blade%2016's%20CPU%2C%20you'll%20want%20to%20overclock%20it%2C%20which%20is%20easy%20to%20do%20through%20the%20pre-installed%20Razer%20Synapse%20app.%20Sure%20enough%2C%20cranking%20the%20CPU%20both%20to%20the%20recommended%20overclock%20speeds%20and%20the%20maximums%20both%20resulted%20in%20much%20better%20Geekbench%20results.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20it's%20a%20shame%20that%20you%20need%20to%20overclock%20the%20CPU%20for%20it%20to%20perform%20better%20than%20a%20weaker%20(and%20far%20cheaper)%20laptop.%20And%20although%20I%20haven't%20seen%20any%20problems%20yet%2C%20I'm%20wary%20that%20heat%20issues%20might%20crop%20up%20from%20constantly%20overclocking%20a%20laptop%20this%20thin.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Cons%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EOther%20design%20flaws%20put%20the%20Razer%20Blade%2016's%20expensive%20price%20in%20question%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20Razer%20Blade%2016%20laptop%20running%20the%20game%20%26quot%3BValorant%2C%26quot%3B%20which%20is%20displaying%20the%20Agent%20page%20for%20the%20character%20Brimstone.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65454dd63cc84b4dfafc5543%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20laptop's%20souped%20up%20hardware%20and%20aesthetics%20come%20at%20a%20high%20price.%3Cp%3EMichael%20Chan%20and%20Paige%20Clarke%2FInsider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3EThat%20CPU%20bottleneck%20isn't%20the%20only%20flaw.%C2%A0%3Cp%3EThe%20Razer%20Blade%2016's%20absolute%20worst%20quality%20is%20its%20trackpad%2C%20which%20feels%20miserable%20to%20use.%20The%20Blade%2016%20trackpad%20constantly%20either%20misses%20clicks%2C%20or%20acts%20like%20you're%20holding%20it%20down%20for%20far%20longer%20than%20you%20actually%20are%2C%20which%20results%20in%20loads%20of%20accidental%20drags%20and%20drops.%20I%20had%20the%20same%20issues%20on%20both%20the%20Blade%2016%20and%2015.%20A