0%E2%80%9Cdeep%20concern%20at%20the%20terrorist%20incidents%2C%20violence%20and%20loss%20of%20civilian%20lives%E2%80%9D%20while%20also%20reiterating%20India%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%9Clongstanding%20and%20consistent%20position%E2%80%9D%20on%20the%20Israel-Palestine%20issue%2C%20the%20statement%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%20%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EGood%20exchange%20of%20perspectives%20with%20President%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fraisi_com%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%40raisi_com%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20Iran%20on%20the%20difficult%20situation%20in%20West%20Asia%20and%20the%20Israel-Hamas%20conflict.%20Terrorist%20incidents%2C%20violence%20and%20loss%20of%20civilian%20lives%20are%20serious%20concerns.%20Preventing%20escalation%2C%20ensuring%20continued%20humanitarian%20aid%20and%E2%80%A6%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%94%20Narendra%20Modi%20(%40narendramodi)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fnarendramodi%2Fstatus%2F1721508502504641014%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3ENovember%206%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cbr%3E%20The%20Iranian%20President%20shared%20with%20Modi%20his%20assessment%20of%20the%20situation%20in%20West%20Asia.%20Both%20leaders%20also%20emphasised%20on%20the%20need%20to%20prevent%20escalation%2C%20ensure%20continued%20humanitarian%20aid%2C%20and%20early%20restoration%20of%20peace%20and%20stability.%20They%20also%20reviewed%20progress%20in%20India-Iran%20bilateral%20cooperation%2C%20and%20%E2%80%9Cwelcomed%20focus%20and%20priority%20accorded%20to%20Chabahar%20port%20in%20Iran%20for%20improving%20regional%20connectivity%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBoth%20sides%20agreed%20to%20remain%20in%20touch%20given%20their%20shared%20interest%20in%20regional%20peace%2C%20security%2C%20and%20stability%2C%20the%20statement%20read.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOver%20the%20past%20few%20days%2C%20Modi%20has%20spoken%20with%20the%20leaders%20of%20Israel%2C%20Jordan%2C%20Egypt%2C%20the%20UK%2C%20and%20the%20United%20Arab%20Emirates%20(UAE)%20to%20discuss%20the%20ongoing%20situation%20in%20West%20Asia.%C2%A0Modi%20had%20first%20spoken%20with%20Israeli%20Prime%20Minister%20Benjamin%20Netanyahu%20to%20reiterate%20%E2%80%9C%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2Fmodi-reiterates-solidarity-phone-call-netanyahu-israel-hamas%5C%22%3Esolidarity%3C%2Fa%3E%E2%80%9D%20with%20the%20Israelis%20on%20October%2010.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EModi%20engaged%20in%20a%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2Fmodi-palestine-authority-president-mahmoud-abbas-call-israel-gaza%5C%22%3Econversation%3C%2Fa%3E%20with%20Palestinian%20Authority%20President%20Mahmoud%20Abbas%20on%20October%2019%2C%20two%20days%20after%20the%20explosion%20at%20Gaza%20City%E2%80%99s%20al-Ahli%20Hospital%20had%20incited%20outrage%20in%20the%20Arab%20world.%20During%20their%20discussion%2C%20Modi%20subtly%20adjusted%20India%E2%80%99s%20position%20by%20reaffirming%20its%20longstanding%20support%20for%20the%20two-state%20solution.%C2%A0The%20third%20regional%20leader%20that%20Modi%20spoke%20with%20on%20Monday%20(October%2023)%20was%20Jordan%E2%80%99s%20King%20Abdullah.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EUnlike%20most%20countries%20in%20the%20global%20south%2C%20India%20has%20refrained%20from%20explicitly%20advocating%20for%20a%20ceasefire%20up%20to%20this%20point.%20However%2C%20the%20mention%20of%20an%20%E2%80%9Cearly%20resolution%E2%80%9D%20appeared%20to%20signify%20a%20shift%20towards%20that%20position.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Israel-Hamas%20conflict%20erupted%20on%20October%207%20when%20Hamas%20militants%20stormed%20into%20Israel%20from%20Gaza%20killed%20more%20than%201%2C400%20people%20and%20took%20some%20240%20others%20hostage.%20Israel%20responded%20with%20a%20campaign%20of%20blistering%20airstrikes%2C%20followed%20by%20a%20ground%20attack%2C%20according%20to%20media%20reports.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20reports%20have%20quoted%20the%20he