2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fdonald-trump-giving-evidence-at-his-civil-trial-in-new-york-13002081%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews-sky-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Fdonald-trump-giving-evidence-at-his-civil-trial-in-new-york-13002081%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Fdonald-trump-giving-evidence-at-his-civil-trial-in-new-york-13002081%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Can%20the%20BJP%20Emerge%20as%20Kingmaker%20in%20Mizoram%20as%20Pollsters%20Predict%20a%20Hung%20Assembly%3F%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F06200114%2FF9deQAsbkAEOZ33.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%E2%80%99s%20(BJP%E2%80%99s)%20rise%20in%20Mizroam%20has%20been%20organic.%20Unlike%20other%20Northeastern%20states%2C%20its%20rise%20in%20Christian-dominated%20Mizoram%20has%20confounded%20political%20pundits.%20While%20Mizoram%20is%20a%20homogenous%20society%20%E2%80%93%20based%20on%20one%20land%20and%20one%20identity%20%E2%80%93%20the%20politics%20of%20the%20state%20is%20based%20on%20a%20binary%20system.%20Of%20the%20two%20dominant%20political%20forces%2C%20one%20is%20known%20for%20its%20ideology%20centered%20around%20Mizo%20nationalism%20while%20the%20other%20is%20known%20for%20its%20secular%20politics%2C%20centered%20around%20Mizo%20Christians.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20Mizoram%2C%20the%20politics%20of%20the%20BJP%20is%20based%20on%20the%20minority%20community%2C%20but%20its%20national%20politics%20is%20based%20on%20the%20majority%20community.%20The%20BJP%20follows%20a%20dual%20approach%20to%20politics%20in%20the%20context%20of%20Mizoram.%20The%20political%20journey%20of%20the%20BJP%20in%20Mizoram%20began%20in%202013%20with%20a%20search%20for%20a%20political%20anchor%20in%20the%20southern%20part%20of%20the%20state.%20However%2C%20the%20BJP%20secured%20fewer%20votes%20than%20those%20cast%20in%20favour%20of%20None%20of%20the%20Above%20(NOTA)%20in%202013.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBy%202018%2C%20the%20BJP%20managed%20to%20obtain%20fourth%20position%20on%20the%20state%E2%80%99s%20political%20landscape%2C%20with%20the%20entry%20of%20its%20first%20MLA%20into%20the%20state%20assembly.%20The%20party%20is%20expected%20to%20outperform%20itself%20this%20time%20around%20when%20the%20state%20goes%20to%20polls%20on%20November%207.%20The%20BJP%20could%20get%20on%20board%20two%20big%20leaders%20from%20other%20parties%20in%20the%20form%20of%20former%20minister%20and%20MLA%20Beichhua%20of%20Mizo%20National%20Front%20and%20the%20speaker%20of%20the%20outgoing%20assembly%20Lalrinliana%20Sailo.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESailo%2C%20who%20won%20the%20Chalfihl%20assembly%20segment%20for%20MNF%20in%202018%2C%20is%20now%20contesting%20from%20the%20Mamit%20constituency%20because%20Chalfihl%20is%20an%20MNF%20stronghold%20and%20known%20to%20have%20an%20anti-BJP%20sentiment%20on%20the%20ground%20to%20hardcore%20Mizo%20voters.%20The%20Mamit%20assembly%20segment%20has%20a%20mix%20of%20voters%20from%20the%20Bru%20and%20Chakma%20communities.%20Sailo%20stands%20a%20chance%20of%20winning%20because%20of%20the%20four-cornered%20contest%20in%20Mamit.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EA%20Bru%20voter%20who%20spoke%20to%20this%20author%20expressed%20confidence%20in%20Sailo%E2%80%99s%20victory%20in%20Mamit.%20%E2%80%9D%20The%20BJP%20and%20its%20leaders%20work%20for%20local%20people.%20Therefore%2C%20Bru%20voters%20have%20hope%20in%20the%20BJP%20and%20we%20will%20vote%20for%20speaker%20Sailo.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EBJP%20versus%20Congress%20in%20MTCs%20and%20ADCs%20areas%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20straight%20between%20the%20BJP%20and%20Congress%20in%20two%20constituencies%20located%20in%20autonomous%20district%20council%20areas%2C%20and%20the%20BJP%20is%20said%20to%20have%20an%20edge%20over%20Congress.%20The%20BJP%20is%20also%20expected%20to%20play%20the%20role%20of%20a%20kingmaker%20in%20case%20of%20a%20hung%20assembly%20%E2%80%93%20a%20prospect%20which%20cannot%20be%20ruled%20out.%20Although%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20rise%20in%20the%20state%20has%20been%20limited%2C%20it%20is%20largely%20due%20to%20the%20decline%20of%20Congress.%20Therefore%2C%20the%20BJP%20is%20expected%20to%20replace%20Congress%20in%20minority%20tribal%20council%20(MTC)%20constituencies%2C%20especially%20in%20three%20autonomous%20district%20councils%20(ADCs)%20this%20time%20around.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThere%20is%20a%20huge%20difference%20between%20the%20way%20Congress%20and%20BJP%20have%20connected%20with%20MTCs%20in%20Mizoram.%20It%20is%20largely%20believed%20that%20Congress%20only%20cares%20about%20MTCs%20until%20it%20is%20in%20power%2C%20and%20when%20in%20opposition%2C%20it%20does%20not%20connect%20with%20the%20MTCs.%20But%2C%20the%20BJP%20is%20said%20to%20maintain%20connection%20with%20MTCs%20at%20all%20times.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EProfessor%20K.%20Robin%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20dichotomy%20between%20the%20BJP%20and%20Congress%20in%20Saiha%2FMara%20ADC%20is%20very%20blurred%20as%20most%20of%20the%20present%20BJP%20leaders%20are%20earlier%20Congress%20cadres.%20There%20are%20very%20few%20new%20BJP%20people%20but%20most%20of%20them%20are%20old%20Congress%20people%20and%20now%20in%20the%20name%20of%20BJP%20in%20southern%20Mizoram%20constituencies.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F06200522%2FF80eu2gWkAATe66.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221079%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F06200522%2FF80eu2gWkAATe66.jpg%201079w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F06200522%2FF80eu2gWkAATe66-300x200.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F06200522%2FF80eu2gWkAATe66-1024x683.jpg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-683782%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22720%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3ERahul%20Gandhi%20at%20a%20rally%20in%20Mizoram.%20Photo%3A%20X%20(Twitter)%2F%40INCMizoram%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3ECongress%20does%20not%20have%20BJP-like%20parental%20organisations%20to%20work%20on%20the%20ground%20at%20all%20times.%C2%A0The%20BJP%20has%20adopted%20a%20three-fold%20political%20strategy%20in%20order%20to%20establish%20itself%20in%20Mizoram%3A%20Political%20objectivity%20and%20subjectivity%2C%20identity%20and%20ideology%2C%20and%20socio-economic%20welfare.%20The%20political%20objective%20of%20the%20BJP%20is%20to%20become%20a%20political%20force%20in%20Mizoram%2C%20and%20MTCs%20are%20its%20political%20subject.%20It%20projects%20itself%20as%20a%20political%20representative%20of%20MTCs%20and%20raises%20their%20issues.%20The%20BJP%20used%20to%20identify%20the%20MTCs%20for%20its%20political%20objective%20and%20to%20promote%20their%20political%20identity.%20Major%20stakes%20for%20the%20BJP%20are%20in%20MTCs%20and%20ADCs.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EProfile%20of%20MTCs%20and%20ADCs%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20four%20MTCs%20are%20Mara%2C%20Lai%2C%20Chakma%2C%20and%20Bru%20(MLCB)%20and%20the%20majority%20of%20these%20live%20in%20their%20respective%20areas%20under%20the%20Autonomous%20District%20Council%20(ADC)%20in%20south%20Mizoram%20bordering%20Myanmar%20and%20Bangladesh.%20A%20significant%20population%20of%20Bru%20(Reang)%20live%20in%20the%20Mamit%20district%20of%20north%20Mizoram%20bordering%20Tripura%20and%20Bangladesh.%20The%20first%20three%20out%20of%20four%20minority%20tribal%20communities%20Mara%2C%20Lai%2C%20Chakma%2C%20and%20Bru%20(Reang)%20have%20their%20separate%20political%20administrative%20area%20recognised%20by%20the%20Autonomous%20District%20Council%20(ADC)%20under%20the%20Sixth%20Schedule%20of%20the%20Constitution%20of%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Bru%20(Reang)%20community%20lives%20in%20non-ADC%20areas%2C%20and%20half%20of%20the%20community%20fled%20to%20Tripura%20after%20ethnic%20violence%20and%20conflict%20erupted%20with%20the%20majority%20Mizo%20ethnic%20community%20in%201997.%20The%20Reang%20community%20has%20been%20demanding%20an%20ADC%20since%20Mizoram%20statehood%2C%20and%20with%20this%20hope%2C%20the%20community%20took%20part%20in%20the%20MNF-led%20insurgency%20in%20the%20state.%20In%201996%2C%20the%20Bru%20(Reang)%20Democratic%20Party%20merged%20with%20the%20BJP%20to%20strengthen%20their%20demand%20for%20ADC.%20Further%2C%20the%20Mara%20Democratic%20Front%20merged%20with%20the%20BJP%20in%202017.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ETargeted%20communities%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20selected%20MTCs%20as%20targeted%20groups%20in%20order%20to%20achieve%20its%20objective%20of%20becoming%20a%20political%20force%20in%20the%20state.%20The%20party%20has%20selected%20four%20minority%20tribal%20communities%3A%20Mara%2C%20Lai%2C%20Chakma%2C%20and%20Bru%20(MLCB)%20in%20the%20southern%20and%20border%20part%20of%20Mizoram%20for%20its%20political%20objective.%20The%20identity%20of%20MTCs%20became%20a%20valued%20currency%20for%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20political%20market.%20The%20party%20highlights%20the%20differences%20between%20minority%20and%20majority%20tribal%20communities%20on%20the%20basis%20of%20their%20distinguished%20identities%20and%20distinct%20histories.%20The%20BJP%20takes%20care%20of%20MTCs%E2%80%99%20socio-economic%20welfare%2C%20whether%20it%20is%20in%20power%20or%20in%20the%20opposition%2C%20and%20always%20maintains%20connections%20and%20contacts%20with%20community%20members%20and%20leaders.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EPolitical%20strategy%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EFor%20the%20BJP%2C%20getting%20big%20leaders%20from%20other%20political%20parties%20has%20proved%20to%20be%20a%20successful%20strategy%20in%20Mizoram.%20In%202018%2C%20for%20the%20first%20time%2C%20it%20was%20in%20the%20form%20of%20Shri%20Hiphei%2C%20seven-time%20Congress%20MLA%20and%20Rajya%20Sabha%20member%2C%20BJP%20began%20this%20approach.%20Hiphei%20got%204%2C000%20votes%20in%20that%20election%20on%20a%20BJP%20ticket%20in%20the%20MTC%20constituency.%20He%20emerged%20as%20the%20first%20powerful%20leader%20of%20the%20BJP%20in%20the%20state%20but%20passed%20away%20during%20the%20COVID-19%20pandemic.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ENext%20year%2C%20the%20Mara%20Democratic%20Front%20merged%20with%20the%20BJP%20and%20the%20party%20formed%20its%20first%20government%20in%20the%20Mara%20ADC%20as%20all%20elected%20executive%20council%20members%20of%20Congress%20joined%20the%20BJP.%20Even%20the%20party%20formed%20its%20alliance%20government%20with%20Congress%20in%20the%20Chakma%20ADC%20in%20early%202022.%20This%20time%20at%20least%20two%20out%20of%20three%20big%20leaders%20of%20other%20parties%20contested%20the%20election%20on%20the%20BJP%20ticket%20and%20had%20a%20good%20chance%20of%20winning.%20As%20a%20Mara%20voter%20Steffi%20C%20Beingiachhiezi%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CThese%20are%20popular%20leaders%20in%20their%20respective%20community%2C%20and%20voters%20follow%20their%20leaders%2C%20no%20matter%20in%20whichever%20party%20they%20are%20in.%E2%80%9D%20A%20Chakma%20voter%20Subh%20Mangal%20Chakma%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CB.D.%20Chakma%20joined%20the%20BJP%20just%20before%20the%202018%20Assembly%20election%20and%20he%20won%20in%20the%20Tuichawng%20constituency%20because%20of%20his%20popularity%20among%20locals.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EState%20government%20versus%20MTCs%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20has%20utilised%20whatever%20opportunity%20came%20in%20the%20MTCs%20and%20ADCs%20politics%20in%20Mizoram.%20The%20party%20stood%20with%20minority%20tribal%20communities%20on%20their%20issues%20with%20the%20state%20government.%20On%20the%20issues%20of%20Bru%20(Reang)%20and%20Chakma%2C%20the%20party%20criticised%20the%20policies%20and%20politics%20of%20the%20ruling%20Mizo%20National%20Front.%20The%20BJP%20convinced%20locals%20about%20the%20failure%20of%20the%20state%20government%20in%20addressing%20the%20issues%20of%20MTCs.%20The%20party%E2%80%99s%20tagline%20is%20a%20BJP-supported%20government%20can%20improve%20the%20governance%2C%20corruption%2C%20development%2C%20and%20implementation%20of%20CSS%20in%20Mizoram.%20The%20BJP%20brought%20the%20MTCs%20into%20the%20national%20mainstream%20politics%20and%20successfully%20mobilised%20and%20polarised%20the%20local%20minority%20communities%20against%20the%20MNF%20government.%20The%20party%20created%20a%20narrative%20that%20the%20MNF%20is%20a%20real%20hindrance%20in%20the%20development%20of%20the%20MTCs%20and%20stability%20and%20governance%20in%20the%20ADC%20region.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ERole%20of%20the%20Central%20BJP%20and%20Union%20government%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20ADC%20communities%20look%20towards%20the%20party%20that%20rules%20at%20the%20Centre.%20The%20BJP%20is%20the%20ruling%20party%20in%20the%20Centre%2C%20therefore%2C%20it%20is%20more%20convenient%20for%20the%20BJP%20to%20establish%20local%20politics%20in%20the%20MTCs%20and%20ADCs.%20Three%20BJP%20Christian%20leaders%20from%20other%20states%20are%20actively%20coordinating%20with%20local%20leaders%20in%20the%20targeted%20MTCs%20and%20ADC%20areas%20long%20before%20the%20election%20schedule%20is%20announced.%20Local%20leaders%20are%20regularly%20visiting%20Delhi%20and%20Guwahati%20to%20consult%20with%20central%20BJP%20leaders%20regarding%20election%20preparations.%20The%20Union%20ministers%20also%20visit%20Mizoram%20to%20meet%20local%20leaders%20and%20discuss%20the%20issues%20of%20Central%20Sponsored%20Schemes%20(CSS)%20in%20Mizoram.%20Every%20Union%20minister%20while%20on%20the%20visit%20of%20Mizoram%20used%20to%20raise%20the%20issue%20of%20misuse%20of%20central%20funds%20and%20sponsored%20schemes%20in%20Mizoram.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EPolitics%2C%20publicity%2C%20and%20propaganda%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20an%20important%20strategy%20of%20the%20BJP%20in%20Mizoram%20and%20elsewhere%20to%20politicise%20the%20issues%20between%20the%20MTCs%2FADCs%20and%20the%20state%20government.%20The%20BJP%20has%20been%20blaming%20the%20state%20government%20on%20the%20matters%20of%20ADCs%2C%20MTCs%2C%20and%20CSS%20in%20Mizoram.%20Publicity%20of%20all%20programmes%20under%20the%20Union%20government%20and%20inauguration%20events%20of%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20is%20largely%20publicised%20by%20the%20state%20unit%20of%20the%20party%20and%20central%20government%20departments%2C%20and%20through%20the%20so-called%20autonomous%20government%20bodies.%20However%2C%20the%20BJP%20leaders%20are%20not%20campaigning%20in%20Aizawl%20city%20because%20of%20its%20failure%20in%20the%20Manipur%20crisis.%20But%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20key%20election%20campaigning%20activities%20are%20only%20in%20Saiha%2C%20Lawngtlai%2C%20and%20Mamit%20constituencies%20where%20the%20BJP%20has%20popular%20candidates.%20BJP%20state%20election%20in-charge%20Kiren%20Rijiju%20once%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CWhichever%20party%20forms%20the%20next%20government%2C%20the%20Deputy%20CM%20will%20be%20of%20BJP.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EElectoral%20strategy%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EJust%20in%20the%20last%20five%20years%2C%20the%20BJP%20has%20raised%20a%20lot%20of%20political%20success%20in%20Mizoram.%20Before%20assembly%20elections%2C%20the%20party%20successfully%20hunted%20three%20popular%20leaders%20of%20other%20parties%2C%20one%20was%20just%20before%20the%202018%20assembly%20election%2C%20and%20two%20this%20time.%20The%20BJP%20formed%20its%20first%20government%20in%20the%20Mara%20ADC%20and%20controlled%20the%20MADC%20politics.%20Presently%2C%20the%20BJP%20is%20the%20second%20leading%20party%20in%20the%20Chakma%20ADC%20and%20it%20also%20formed%20a%20coalition%20government%20with%20Congress%20for%20a%20short%20time.%20The%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20electoral%20strategy%20is%20to%20become%20a%20strong%20opposition%20force%20in%20the%20ADC%20and%20MTC%20areas.%20The%20BJP%20succeeded%20in%20making%20a%20dent%20(as%20party%20defection)%20in%20other%20parties%20especially%20in%20Congress%20in%20the%20Mara%20ADC%20as%20all%20elected%20Congress%20executive%20councillors%20joined%20the%20BJP%20in%202019.%20The%20party%20promoted%20its%20first%20MLA%20Dr%20B%20D%20Chakma%20to%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20national%20executive%20council%20as%20a%20member%3B%20however%2C%20he%20is%20not%20contesting%20the%20election%20this%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESocio-economic%20relations%20with%20MTCs%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20has%20good%20relations%20with%20the%20local%20minority%20tribal%20communities%20such%20as%20Mara%2C%20Lai%2C%20Chakma%20and%20Bru%20(Reang).%20The%20party%20does%20not%20only%20have%20political%20but%20socio-economic%20relations%20with%20local%20communities.%20The%20local%20politics%20of%20the%20BJP%20is%20led%20by%20the%20popular%20local%20social%20or%20business%20leaders.%20The%20popular%20face%20as%20a%20social%20activist%20or%20businessman%20or%20civil%20society%20leader%20or%20influential%20community%20leader%20especially%20youth%20will%20lead%20to%20the%20socio-economic%20activities%20of%20the%20party.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ELike%20Mara%20social%20activist%20Delson%20Notlia%20is%20key%20channel%20leader%20between%20the%20central%20party%20leadership%20and%20local%20party%20organisation.%20Notlia%20is%20a%20national%20secretary%20of%20the%20minority%20cell%20of%20BJP%20in%20Mizoram%3B%20he%20is%20well%20guided%20by%20regional%20leaders%20such%20as%20Hemanta%20Biswas%20Sarma%20and%20John%20Barla.%20The%20BJP%20provides%20help%20and%20assistance%20to%20suffering%20people%2C%20vehicle%20service%20to%20accident%20victims%2C%20helps%20poor%20families%20in%20ration%20card%20allotment%20and%20other%20welfare%20schemes%2C%20document%20preparation%2C%20widow%20women%2C%20and%20female%20head%20of%20families.%20The%20BJP%20has%20provided%20assistance%20as%20food%20and%20medicines%20with%20help%20of%20MTP%20(Mara%20Youth%20Association)%20during%20the%20Covid-19%20pandemic.%20The%20party%20helps%20local%20communities%20through%20banking%20facilities%20medical%20services%20and%20schools.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EConclusion%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20is%20fully%20confident%20of%20winning%20two%20constituencies%20this%20time.%20Adding%20one%20Saiha%20and%20retaining%20Tuichawng.%20Whether%20it%20wins%2C%20the%20party%20is%20expected%20to%20take%20second%20place%20in%20the%20Palak%20and%20Mamit%20constituencies.%20This%20time%20a%20number%20of%20central%20BJP%20leaders%20visited%20three%20constituencies%20Mamit%2C%20Saiha%2C%20and%20Tuichawng%2C%20but%20no%20one%20visited%20any%20constituency%20in%20Aizawl%20City.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20contested%2023%20seats%20and%20state%20party%20president%20Vanlalhmuaka%20is%20contesting%20from%20the%20Dampa%20constituency%20on%20the%20border%20with%20Bangladesh%20and%20Tripura%2C%20which%20has%20significant%20Bru%20and%20Chakma%20voters.%20Some%20political%20pundits%20in%20Mizoram%20believe%20that%20the%20BJP%20has%20secret%20post-poll%20alliances%20with%20the%20Zoram%20People%E2%80%99s%20Movement%20and%20MNF.%20The%20party%20is%20said%20to%20be%20putting%20up%20a%20friendly%20contest%20against%20MNF%20in%20south%20Mizoram%20and%20ZPM%20in%20north%20Mizoram.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20event%20of%20a%20hung%20assembly%20result%2C%20the%20BJP%20is%20expected%20to%20become%20a%20king-maker.%20The%20Manipur%20issue%20has%20negatively%20impacted%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20prospects%20in%20north%20Mizoram%2C%20but%20due%20to%20two%20big%20leaders%20joining%20the%20party%20just%20before%20the%20elections%2C%20it%20is%20giving%20a%20tough%20fight%20to%20Congress%20in%20south%20Mizoram.%20For%20the%20BJP%2C%20the%20fight%20is%20against%20Congress%2C%20not%20as%20much%20against%20MNF%20or%20ZPM.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ESuwa%20Lal%20Jangu%20is%20an%20Assistant%20Professor%2C%20Political%20Science%20Department%2C%20Mizoram%20University.%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1699281732000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F06200114%2FF9deQAsbkAEOZ33.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fcan-the-bjp-emerge-as-kingmaker-in-mizoram-as-pollsters-predict-a-hung-assembly%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22For%20the%20BJP%2C%20the%20fight%20is%20against%20Congress%2C%20not%20as%20much%20against%20Mizo%20National%20Front%20or%20Zoram%20People's%20Movement.%20The%20party%20is%20confident%20of%20winning%20Saiha%20assembly%20segment%20and%20retaining%20Tuichawng%20constituency%2C%20though%20it%20is%20contesting%2023%20seats.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A4%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fcan-the-bjp-emerge-as-kingmaker-in-mizoram-as-pollsters-predict-a-hung-assembly%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Kidnappers%20warn%20release%20of%20Luis%20Diaz's%20father%20at%20risk%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1699281240000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fe3.365dm.com%2F23%2F11%2F768x432%2Fskynews-luis-diaz-liverpool_6349890.jpg%3F20231106160913%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fluis-diaz-kidnappers-in-colombia-warn-release-of-liverpool-stars-father-could-be-delayed-13002060%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Colombian%20rebels%20allegedly%20behind%20the%20kidnapping%20of%20Liverpool%20star%20Luis%20Diaz's%20father%20have%20warned%20his%20planned%20release%20is%20at%20risk%20and%20could%20now%20be%20delayed.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A6%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fluis-diaz-kidnappers-in-colombia-warn-release-of-liverpool-stars-father-could-be-delayed-13002060%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews-sky-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2