%2C%20and%20the%20Saw%20Scaled%20Viper.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3EAfter%20digging%20into%20the%20root%20causes%2C%20he%20found%20that%20people%20in%20the%20region%20cultivate%20crops%20like%20soybean%2C%20groundnuts%2C%20and%20sugarcane%20throughout%20the%20year%2C%20which%20makes%20them%20prone%20to%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F172628%2Ftelangana-police-hero-snake-rescue-india%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esnake%20encounters%20%3C%2Fa%3Eoften.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20India%2C%20around%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.who.int%2Findia%2Fhealth-topics%2Fsnakebite%23%3A~%3Atext%3DSnakebite%2520in%2520India%2C-The%2520World%2520Health%26amp%3Btext%3DPublished%2520reports%2520suggest%2520that%2520between%2Camputations%2520and%2520other%2520permanent%2520disabilities.%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E90%20percent%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20snakebites%20are%20caused%20by%20the%20%E2%80%98big%20four%E2%80%99%20%E2%80%94%20Common%20krait%2C%20Indian%20cobra%2C%20Russell%E2%80%99s%20viper%2C%20and%20the%20Saw%20Scaled%20Viper.%20If%20there%20is%20a%20delay%20in%20administering%20the%20anti-snake%20venom%2C%20Dr%20Sadanand%20says%2C%20chances%20are%20the%20snake%20bite%20will%20cause%20grave%20organ%20damage%2C%20or%20prove%20to%20be%20fatal.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOther%20than%20this%2C%20he%20adds%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20realised%20that%20usually%20critically%20ill%20patients%20had%20to%20go%20to%20cities%20for%20treatment%20as%20there%20was%20no%20ambulance%20or%20support%20at%20the%20local%20level.%20As%20a%20result%2C%20many%20would%20die%20on%20their%20way%20to%20the%20hospital.%20Those%20who%20could%20not%20go%20to%20the%20city%20would%20visit%20faith%20healers%20and%20waste%20the%20golden%20hour%20for%20the%20treatment.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20also%20found%20that%20medical%20officers%20at%20the