t%20petition%20by%20one%20Magesh%20Karthikeyan%20seeking%20directions%20to%20local%20police%20to%20grant%20permission%20for%20a%20%E2%80%9Cmeeting%20about%20Dravidian%20ideology%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EKarthikeyan%20had%20suggested%20a%20Tamil%20title%20for%20his%20meeting%20which%20roughly%20translates%20to%20%E2%80%98Dravida%20Eradication%20and%20Tamilian%20Integration%20Conclave%E2%80%99.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20he%20filed%20his%20writ%20petition%20in%20light%20of%20an%20earlier%20order%20passed%20by%20the%20high%20court%2C%20which%20directed%20police%20to%20permit%20a%20meeting%20whose%20conveners%20may%20have%20contrarian%20views%20on%20Dravidian%20ideology.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20bench%20said%20this%20earlier%20meeting%20and%20Karthikeyan%E2%80%99s%20proposed%20meeting%20were%20different%20kettles%20of%20fish.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20petitioner%20herein%20claims%20that%20it%20is%20%5Bhis%5D%20fundamental%20right%20to%20conduct%20such%20%5Ba%5D%20meeting.%20The%20court%20cannot%20subscribe%20to%20this%20view%2C%E2%80%9D%20its%20order%20read.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIt%20continued%3A%20%E2%80%9CNo%20person%20in%20this%20country%20can%20have%20a%20right%20to%20propagate%20divisive%20ideas%20and%20conduct%20%5Bmeetings%5D%20to%20abolish%20or%20eradicate%20any%20ideology.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20Read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fbjp-attacking-udhayanidhi-stalin-over-sanatana-dharma-remarks%5C%22%3EThe%20BJP%20May%20End%20Up%20Tying%20Itself%20in%20Knots%20By%20Attacking%20Udhayanidhi%20Stalin%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CNo%20one%20can%20expect%20courts%20to%20aid%20them%20to%20propagate%20ideas%20to%20create%20ill-will%20among%20the%20public%20%E2%80%A6%20If%20the%20request%20of%20the%20petitioner%20is%20acceded%2C%20it%20will%20cause%20further%20disturbance%20to%20the%20peace%20and%20tranquillity%20of%20the%20public%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20bench%E2%80%99s%20order%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIt%20also%20rebuked%20the%20organisers%20of%20the%20September%202%20%E2%80%98%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.oxfordreference.com%2Fdisplay%2F10.1093%2Foi%2Fauthority.20110803100439799%5C%22%3ESanatana%3C%2Fa%3E%20Eradication%20Conclave%E2%80%99.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CSome%20members%20of%20the%20ruling%20party%20%5Bthe%20DMK%5D%20and%20ministers%20participated%20in%20the%20meeting%20held%20for%20eradicating%20%E2%80%98Sanatana%20Dharma%E2%80%99%20and%20no%20action%20has%20been%20taken%20by%20the%20police%20against%20them%2C%20which%20is%20a%20dereliction%20of%20duty%20on%20the%20part%20of%20the%20police%2C%E2%80%9D%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EPeople%20%E2%80%9Care%20already%20fed%20up%20by%20the%20way%20some%20of%20the%20fringe%20groups%20in%20support%20of%20persons%20who%20have%20taken%20the%20oath%20of%20office%20to%20preserve%20the%20spirit%20of%20%5Bthe%5D%20constitution%2C%20act%20in%20breach%20of%20their%20oath%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20bench%20claimed%20in%20its%20order.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20court%20is%20of%20the%20view%20that%20%5Ba%5D%20person%20in%20power%20should%20realise%20the%20danger%20of%20speech%20unflaring%20%5Bsic%5D%20fissiparous%20tendency%20and%20behave%20responsibly%20and%20restrain%20themselves%20from%20propagating%20views%20which%20will%20divide%20people%20in%20the%20name%20of%20ideology%2C%20caste%20and%20religion.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CInstead%20they%20may%20concentrate%20on%20eradicating%20intoxicating%20drinks%20and%20drugs%20which%20are%20injuries%20to%20health%2C%20corruption%20untouchability%20and%20other%20social%20%5Bevils%5D%2C%E2%80%9D%20it%20concluded%20before%20dismissing%20Karthikeyan%E2%80%99s%20writ%20petition.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20September%202%20meeting%2C%20Udhayanidhi%20Stalin%20%E2%80%93%20who%20is%20also%20the%20son%20of%20Tamil%20Nadu%20chief%20minister%20and%20party%20president%20M.K.%20Stalin%20%E2%80%93%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthepri