Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20blasting%20operations%20often%20induce%20ground%20vibration%20inside%20the%20mine.%20Strong%20vibrations%20damage%20the%20structure%20and%20result%20in%20ceiling%20collapse.%20We%20frequently%20witnessed%20mishaps.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHe%20continues%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20remember%20it%20was%20the%20day%20of%20%3Cem%3EMaghi%20Purnima%20%3C%2Fem%3E(auspicious%20full%20moon%20day)%20when%20one%20of%20my%20friends%20from%20the%20village%20was%20inside%20the%20coal%20mine.%20Due%20to%20the%20strong%20vibrations%2C%20a%20ceiling%20collapsed%20and%20he%20got%20trapped%20inside.%20We%20later%20found%20him%20dead%3B%20his%20body%20was%20crushed%2C%E2%80%9D%20shares%20Diganta.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EDiganta%20Das%2C%20a%20manual%20labour%20of%20Pkg%20food%20industry%20of%20South%20India%2C%20returned%20home%20during%20Covid%20%26amp%3B%20dared%20to%20open%20small%20packaged%20Parota%20making%20units%20in%20Biswanath%20Chariali%20%26amp%3B%20Lakhimpur%2C%20churning%20out%20avg%201200%20packets%20daily%20at%20each%20centre%20capturing%20market%20from%20Tezpur%20to%20Tinsukia.%201%2F3%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FmBzcV5sdEV%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FmBzcV5sdEV%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%E2%80%94%20Mrinal%20Talukdar%20(%40mrinaltalukdar8)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fmrinaltalukdar8%2Fstatus%2F1640331493384790016%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EMarch%2027%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%20%20%3Cp%3EThis%20incident%20left%20him%20devastated%20and%20he%20decided%20to%20pack%20his%20bag%20and%20go%20home.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESoon%20after%2C%20he%20left%20for%20Sikkim%20where%20he%20started%20working%20again%20as%20a%20construction%20worker.%20After%20two%20more%20years%2C%20he%20decided%20to%20move%20to%20Bengaluru.%20%E2%80%9CMost%20of%20the%20youth%20from%20our%20state%20go%20to%20cities%20like%20Delhi%2C%20Bengaluru%2C%20and%20Pune%20for%20work.%20I%20had%20always%20wanted%20to%20see%20Bengaluru%2C%20so%20I%20moved%20there%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHe%20secured%20the%20work%20of%20a%20security%20guard%20in%20the%20city%20for%20a%20monthly%20salary%20of%20Rs%204%2C500%2C%20but%20amid%20low%20salary%20and%20untimely%20payments%2C%20he%20eventually%20quit%20that%20work%20too.%20%E2%80%9CI%20did%20not%20have%20a%20problem%20in%20working%20hard%2C%20but%20I%20wished%20to%20earn%20a%20decent%20income%20for%20all%20the%20hard%20work%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ELater%20on%2C%20Diganta%20worked%20as%20a%20cook%20in%20Guwahati%20until%20he%20secured%20a%20job%20as%20a%20mixing%20man%20in%20a%20food%20manufacturing%20unit%20in%20Mangaluru.%20The%20exposure%20helped%20him%20understand%20the%20nitty-gritty%20of%20the%20food%20production%20industry.%20And%20soon%2C%20he%20was%20offered%20the%20job%20of%20a%20%3Cem%3Eparatha%3C%2Fem%3E%20maker.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EJust%20when%20he%20thought%20things%20were%20improving%2C%20he%20met%20with%20an%20accident.%20In%202017%2C%20he%20was%20left%20paralysed%20after%20a%20high-voltage%20electric%20cable%20fell%20on%20him.%20%E2%80%9CI%20had%20to%20return%20to%20my%20village.%20That%20was%20the%20toughest%20phase%20of%20my%20life%20as%20I%20was%20without%20work%20for%20so%20many%20months%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Diganta%20adding%20that%20it%20took%20almost%20two%20years%20for%20him%20to%20completely%20recover.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Fparota-2-1699019138.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22These%20parathas%20are%20characterised%20by%20their%20crispy%2C%20flaky%2C%20soft%2C%20and%20multi-layered%20texture.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads