d%20he%20wanted%20more%20from%20life%20than%20a%20corner%20cabin%20and%20its%20perks.%C2%A0%20During%20a%20business%20trip%20to%20London%2C%20he%20spent%20the%20major%20part%20of%20his%20days%20exploring%20the%20city%2C%20going%20on%20heritage%20walks%2C%20and%20wondering%20why%20India%20lacked%20these%20experiences.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOn%20returning%20to%20Bengaluru%2C%20the%20feeling%20of%20diving%20into%20something%20creative%20overtook%20him.%20He%20bade%20goodbye%20to%20the%20corporate%20world%20and%20started%20%E2%80%98Bangalore%20Walks%E2%80%99%2C%20literally%20and%20figuratively%20taking%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F304444%2Foddar-community-keeps-thammampatti-tamil-nadu-art-alive-for-decades-video%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20road%20less%20travelled%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOver%20the%20years%2C%20these%20walks%20have%20given%20the%20residents%20of%20the%20metropolis%20as%20well%20as%20celebrated%20personalities%20a%20chance%20to%20fall%20in%20love%20with%20the%20city%E2%80%99s%20unseen%20side.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%20early%20years%20of%20starting%2C%20Pai%20began%20to%20be%20identified%20as%20the%20man%20who%20showed%20up%20every%20Sunday%20morning%20at%207%20on%20Bengaluru%E2%80%99s%20MG%20Road%20ready%20to%20begin%20his%20signature%20three-hour-long%20%E2%80%98Victorian%20Bangalore%20Walk%E2%80%99.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ECome%20rain%20or%20shine%2C%20this%20was%20a%20weekly%20ritual.%20And%20the%20number%20of%20people%20who%20turned%20up%20never%20deterred%20his%20spirit.%20%E2%80%9CSometimes%20it%20was%20a%20handful%2C%20other%20times%20a%20crowd.%E2%80%9D%20But%20Pai%20saw%20to%20it%20that%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F289457%2Findia-museums-travel-city-culture-history-must-visit%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20show%20went%20o%3C%2Fa%3En.%20And%20today%2C%20he%20has