3%2F11%2FWith-Amitabh-Kant-3-1698935236-157x300.jpg%20157w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2FWith-Amitabh-Kant-3-1698935236-150x287.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-333508%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22887%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EArun%20Pai%20with%20India%E2%80%99s%20Sherpa%20Amitabh%20Kant%20at%20the%20G20%20Summit%2C%20Picture%20source%3A%20Arun%20Pai%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20walks%20do%20not%20have%20a%20set%20theme%2C%20Pai%20improvises%20along%20the%20way%20depending%20on%20the%20audience%20he%20is%20catering%20to.%20And%20he%20delivers%20every%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EToday%2C%20the%20model%20caters%20to%20specific%20groups%20as%20opposed%20to%20public%20walks.%20A%20group%20of%2025%20individuals%20from%20a%20policy%20think%20tank%20in%20the%20city%20who%20recently%20attended%20one%20of%20the%20walks%20will%20agree.%20After%20three%20hours%20spent%20covering%20what%20they%20thought%20were%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F185733%2Fkolkata-kumortuli-mud-sculptures-tradition-durga-puja-heritage-india%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efamiliar%20areas%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20city%20centre%2C%20(near%20their%20office)%2C%20the%20group%20was%20enthralled%20by%20this%20new%20lens%20through%20which%20they%20were%20seeing%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EFor%20Pai%2C%20it%20was%20the%20same%20route%20he%20took%20with%20all%20his%20groups%2C%20but%20the%20storytelling%20differed.%20%E2%80%9CAs%20there%20were%20retired%20army%20personnel%20and%20defence%20strategists%20in%20the%20group%2C%20I%20ended%20up%20talking%20about%20the%20military%20DNA%20of%20Bangalore%20more%20than%20I%20would%20to%20a%20bunch%20of%20school%20children%20for%20whom%20that%20is%20not%20so%20exciting.%20So%20you%20see%2C%20the%20slant%20changes.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20his%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F184025%2Fchennai-man-maritime-museum-lighthouse-heritage-inspiring-india%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efavourite%20stories%3C%2Fa%3E%20along%20the%20walks%20is%20narrating%20about%20the%20%E2%80%9Cdramatic%E2%80%9D%20Battle%20of%20Bangalore%20that%20took%20place%20in%201791.%20After%20mortal%20combat%20with%20Tipu%20Sultan%E2%80%99s%20army%2C%20the%20Bangalore%20Fort%20was%20captured%2C%20leaving%20thousands%20of%20Mysoreans%20dead.%20%E2%80%9CPeople%20know%20of%20the%20Battle%20of%20Panipat%20and%20Plassey%20but%20not%20this%20event%2C%20which%20had%20an%20equally%20large%20impact%20on%20India%2C%20if%20not%20more%2C%E2%80%9D%20notes%20Pai.%20He%20adds%2C%20%E2%80%9CThis%20is%20an%20interesting%20story%20of%20the%20role%20the%20fall%20of%20Bengaluru%20played%20in%20our%20history%2C%20and%20I%20tell%20it%20in%20such%20a%20fashion%20that%20people%20want%20to%20learn%20more%20about%20it.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EEvery%20story%20picked%20up%20by%C2%A0%20Pai%20%E2%80%94%20the%20lores%20of%20the%20city%E2%80%99s%20churches%2C%20the%20mapping%20of%20India%20that%20began%20in%20the%20city%20%E2%80%94%20has%20global%20appeal%20and%20is%20infused%20with%20personal%20anecdotes.%20Often%20in%20the%20course%20of%20the%20walk%2C%20Pai%20gets%20asked%20about%20the%20%E2%80%9CChristmas%20trees%E2%80%9D%20that%20line%20the%20roads.%20He%20then%20stops%20and%20narrates%20how%20they%20came%20to%20be.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CDid%20you%20know%20they%20are%20actually%20from%20New%20Zealand%3F%E2%80%9D%20he%20asks%20me.%20I%20didn%E2%80%99t.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThese%2060-foot%20trees%20are%20so%20prevalent%20these%20days%20that%20most%20people%20think%20they%20are%20native%20to%20the%20city.%20But%20it%20is%20interesting%20to%20know%20that%20they%20were%20brought%20here%20almost%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F182026%2Fmughal-miniatures-stunning-street-art-photo-story-india%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E200%20years%20ago%3C%2Fa%3E%20as%20part%20of%20a%20massive%20botanical%20experiment%20by%20British%20and%20Indian%20scientists.%20They%20were%20trying%20to%20understand%20how%20to%20classify%20the%20world%E2%80%99s%20trees%20and%20plants%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20informs.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CSince%20the%20city%20is%20not%20too%20high%2C%20not%20too%20low%2C%20not%20too%20wet%2C%20not%20too%20dry%2C%20it%20turned%20out%20to%20be%20a%20conducive%20environment%20for%20these%20very%20foreign%20trees%20to%20grow.%20Today%20these%20%E2%80%98Christmas%20trees%E2%80%99%20(Norfolk%20Island%20Pines)%20have%20acclimatised%20to%20this%20climate%20and%20soil%20and%20have%20become%20local.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EPai%20has%20narrated%20these%20and%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F144331%2Fasi-finds-copper-bronze-age-chariots-tombs-up-village%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eother%20stories%20of%20the%20city%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20some%20of%20the%20most%20influential%20people%20%E2%80%94%20including%20global%20MD%20of%20McKinsey%20Dominic%20Barton%2C%20president%20of%20Microsoft%20Brad%20Smith%2C%20Infosys%20founder%20NR%20Narayanamurthy%2C%20India%E2%80%99s%20Chief%20Economic%20Advisor%20Anantha%20Nageswaran%2C%C2%A0US%20Digital%20Ambassador%20Nathaniel%20Fick%2C%20former%20PM%20of%20Australia%20Kevin%20Rudd%20and%20comedian%20Trevor%20Noah.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAs%20Nageswaran%20recounts%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20was%20so%20happy%20that%20my%20friends%20from%20iSPIRT%20arranged%20for%20me%20to%20join%20Arun%20Pai%E2%80%99s%20Bengaluru%20walk%20on%2024%20July.%20He%20was%20simply%20brilliant%20with%20his%20erudition%2C%20wit%2C%20and%20deep%20understanding%20of%20the%20history%20of%20the%20world%2C%20the%20country%2C%20and%20the%20city.%20His%20pride%20in%20being%20a%20Bangalorean%20came%20through%20so%20well%20that%20I%20was%20infected%20with%20that%20pride.%20He%20made%20Sir%20M%20Visweswaraiya%20and%20the%20Mysore%20Maharaja%20come%20alive%20with%20his%20vivid%20descriptions%20of%20their%20vision%20and%20their%20contributions%20to%20the%20city%20and%20the%20country.%20It%20was%20a%20perfect%20start%20to%20the%20day%20and%20made%20my%20short%20visit%20to%20Bengaluru%20entirely%20memorable.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBut%20in%20the%20midst%20of%20this%20adulation%2C%20one%20experience%20outshines%20it%20all%20%E2%80%94%20India%E2%80%99s%20Presidency%20of%20the%20G20%20Summit%20in%202023.%20Karnataka%20played%20host%20to%20over%2010%20important%20summit%20meetings%20over%20the%20year%20including%20the%20G20%20Summit.%20And%20Pai%20was%20the%20official%20representative%20of%20the%20Government%20of%20Karnataka%20for%20designing%20and%20planning%20the%20city%20tours%20and%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F127339%2Fcalcutta-houses-instagram-photo-project%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eexcursions%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20the%20last%20detail%20%E2%80%94%20including%20sites%20around%20cities%20like%20Mysuru%2C%20Hampi%2C%20and%20Bengaluru.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ERecalling%20the%20experience%20at%20Hampi%2C%20Pai%20says%20it%20was%20phenomenal.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COver%20the%20course%20of%20the%20three%20days%2C%20I%20highlighted%20globally%20relevant%20stories%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20history%2C%20culture%20and%20society%20to%20over%20200%20delegates%C2%A0from%2020%20countries.%20We%20were%20given%20a%20clear%20task%20by%20Amitabh%20Kant%20%E2%80%94%20India%E2%80%99s%20Sherpa.%20He%20wanted%20us%20to%20provide%20the%20right%20context%2C%20background%20and%20experiences%20so%20that%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F119531%2Fall-you-need-to-know-about-kashmirs-famous-pashmina%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esplend