iving%20life%20in%20greener%20ways.%20I%20have%20contributed%20to%20several%20non-profits%20across%20the%20country%20by%20talking%20about%20eco-friendly%20ways%20of%20living%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20civil%20engineer%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CHowever%2C%20at%20a%20personal%20level%2C%20I%20always%20experienced%20a%20gap%20between%20preaching%20such%20practices%20and%20implementing%20them%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%20So%20when%20presented%20with%20the%20chance%20to%20materialise%20his%20vision%2C%20the%2057-year-old%20dedicated%20his%20efforts%20to%20building%20a%20home%20that%20embodied%20his%20principles%20of%20responsible%20citizenship%20and%20sustainable%20living.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMore%20than%20a%20decade%20ago%2C%20in%202011%2C%20Ramachandrudu%20bought%20a%20piece%20of%20land%20and%20constructed%20a%20home%20spanning%202%2C700%20square%20feet.%20Within%20the%20open%20area%2C%20he%20cultivated%2040%20varieties%20of%20trees%20%E2%80%94%20including%20mango%2C%20orange%2C%20papaya%2C%20chikoo%2C%20banana%2C%20and%20jackfruit%2C%20as%20well%20as%2010%20types%20of%20hibiscus.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2Fsustainable-home-2-1698759550.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22What%E2%80%99s%20noteworthy%20is%20that%20the%20entire%20structure%20is%20crafted%20from%20recycled%20materials%20like%20cycle%20rims%2C%20old%20glass%20doors%2C%20and%20shipping%20containers.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2Fsustainable-home-2-1698759550.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2Fsustainable-home-2-1698759550-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2Fsustainable-home-2-1698759550-50